product_title: Fun Daisy New Design Jewelry Vintage Grand Choker Rhinestones Fashion Necklace
review_headline: Beautiful statement piece, great quality, great price!
review_body: This is the first time I've ordered anything like this through Amazon. The photos that others posted in their reviews helped, but it is much nicer in person. The photos don't do it justice. It's a heavy piece, but not too heavy. It has the right weight to it for something with that many stones in it. If it was lighter, I would have worried about the quality - but this is not the case. For the price, this is perfect - probably even better than I expected! The stones have a lot of sparkle to them, but it's hard to get that in a photo. This is a striking piece.The necklace has varied shades of blue, so it could go with many different blue clothing pieces, or go well with something contrasting. The metal has an antique brass look to it. It looks like something you'd find in a higher end boutique.  I have no doubt this will be a great statement piece for everyday or for a special event look. I'm very glad I took a chance and bought this one. This was an awesome find! I can't say enough good things about it! If you purchase, I don't think you'll be disappointed. Fun Daisy also packed this very securely in a cute box and bubble wrap inside. It arrived, no damage, in perfect condition.

product_title: A Pair Nipple rings Flower shape Nickel free nipple shield Copper fashion women body piercing jewelry
review_body:
The rings arrived with a velvet pouch and an alcohol swab for cleaning which was very nice. However, after one use, the stones started falling out. I was able to catch some or pull some out myself and super glue them in place but most of them have been lost. It was disappointing. It was also disappointing to find out that I was injured after the first use. My nipples were very sore and I thought it was because I had not used them properly. After handling the rings more and looking closely, I noticed that there were metal tags on the ends of the rings that ended up cutting into my skin. They look really nice on when they have all the stones in.

product_title: Cavalier Jewelers 8MM Cobalt Chrome Ring Wedding Band - Flat Brushed Top and Polished Finish Edges
review_body:
I got married a few weeks ago and I really like this ring. My fiancee and I scoured around 15 different jewelry shops to look for our wedding bands. I noticed that the mens' bands made from alternative metals were very good in most shops , and in the range of 250-300 dollars. That's already a huge difference from what you'd pay for a white gold or platinum ring. However, most of these alternative metal bands displayed in the shops were size 10 (the standard display size) and given that these rings couldn't be resized they told me I would have to wait 1 or 2 weeks to order them.

That's how I started to check out rings online. All I really wanted was a clean, beveled cobalt ring. This ring by Cavalier looks just as good as those I've seen in the shops. The price is unbelievable. I prefer cobalt over tungsten because it has a brighter look that almost resembles white gold. This ring has a very nice texture and I kinda play with it often just as Gollum played with the Ring. I also quite like the fact that the only word in the inside of the ring is "cobalt" and none of those fancy phrases such as "brute" etc. or a huge brand name that you'll find in other rings.

Please keep up the good work Cavalier Jewelers!

product_title: HZman Mens Silver Stainless Steel Gothic Skull Pendant Necklace,24 Inch Rounded Box Chain Style
review_headline: It's a lot bigger that I thought it would be.
review_body: I have no idea why I giggled the way that I did when I took this out of its package. For some reason, the bottom of the schools nose looks like a heart, and the rest of the base is kind of scary looking, so that's probably why I started to laugh. It's like, you can't be scary and have a heart on your face.  The details that come on this little scary fella are pretty cool, I like how at the top of the head they have a design where it's like a brain, with the school circle going around it. I mean, I like it, but it's creepy. But! He has a heart on his nose so it's OK.  It has a great necklace, it's 24 inches long of surgical stainless steel, that's a really good links for a man. The necklace is a round ish shape, but they are links. I think that's actually really nice because hair won't get cotton tangled into it.  OK, the school freaks me out. I think it's the teeth. Why does a skeleton have perfect teeth? Do you think that those would've at least been a little rotted, so he looks like a fresh school face. I think that's what freaks me out. Even though he has a heart on his nose, I still don't want to stare at it.  If your dude likes skulls, creepy skulls??? This is for him. If YOU don't like creepy looking school pendants, don't get it. Because it's creepy. It's definitely Gothic! The gift bag it came in was really nice. :-)  I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do the review on my own.

product_title: 925 Sterling Silver Rhodium Plated 3-6mm Plain Hollow Silver Ball Screwback Baby Girls Earrings
review_headline: poor quality, not worth the money
review_body:
I purchased other earrings from this company a while ago and they've been great, I leave them in all the time and I've never had a problem with them. I have two holes in each ear so I thought I'd go with these simple earrings for the second set.

When I received these earrings I took them out of the packaging and tried to take the screwback off the earring and it snapped in half. I hardly applied any pressure at all and I've never had earrings break like this. I didn't even bother trying to take the back off the second earring. I returned them through amazon and figured I'd give them the benefit of the doubt and get a replacement pair. The second pair came (thankfully really painless return/replacement process) and I noticed one earring was slightly bent. I tried to take the screwback off and fix the bend but ultimately I just didn't like how bendy the earrings were, especially since I sleep in mine. For $14 I expect better quality, like the other pair of CZ earrings I got from this company.

This charm is well worth the price. This would be a great birthday gift for someone.

* The chains are different than portrayed; less dainty and cheaper looking (the long strand doesn't have the knots in it like shown)

product_title: 55 Pcs. Costume Jewelry Mix-lot. (Zebra Accessories Brand)
review_headline: I'm torn on whether this was a good deal or not
review_body: I bought this to help fill up my jewelry booth at a local vendor store. You get a ton of stuff.  Some is really cute, and some is hideous.  I'd say about 65 percent is cute.  However, a large majority of it looks really cheap, which is probably why the price is so decent per piece.  I noticed some packaging issues with the Zebra cards a lot of the pieces come on.  The earring holes were not lined up. One would be up higher than the other and it was just weird. I also noticed some of the post earrings did not have post backings, but the rubber tips that are often used to keep fishhook style earrings from falling off the card.  I'm going to put the hideous pieces together into a bag and try to sell it as Halloween costume jewelry.  I'm torn on whether this was a good deal or not, I guess my sales at the store will tell all.

product_title: 14k Gold Italian Tri-Color Twist Hoop Earrings
review_body:
I gave these to my wife to wear and she promptly announced that the earrings are "light, beautiful and easy to wear."

Usually her ears are very sensitive to metal and she has to be very careful when picking out earrings, but these don't generally irritate her ears (and when her ears do get irritated she doesn't think it is the earrings that are doing it.)

She has even worn these earrings to bed without remembering that she had them in, they were so comfortable. I was pretty impressed by that, because these are not just studs or little hoops.

So these are not only very attractive (my judgment here) but they're practical and comfortable. She has even asked her chiropractor about having them on when getting an adjustment and he said that they didn't get in the way while he was adjusting her neck, so they are, she says, the perfect set to own.

Her verdict: she would absolutely get another pair something happened to these.

product_title: 10mm Created Alexandrite & Zirconia Round Ring .925 Sterling Silver Rhodium Finish
review_body: My husband got this for me & it was special because it was a token of his love, as we have been apart for a long time. The Alexandrite fell out within hours of putting it on. We immediately let Elizabeth Jewelry Inc. know, & they said,"You can send the ring back and I can have a new alexandrite set in the ring.  It will cost $20.  This is our cost for the repairs.  I will have the ring brand new and ship it back to you for free." My husband thought that was unsatisfactory & explained that $20 + s&h is as much as the ring! After what felt like convincing them, we sent it back to them; they sent a new one & it appears to be set in the prongs better & hopefully won't fall out again. I was really upset & looked everywhere for it so I could attempt to set it back in place myself. After that, Elizabeth Jewelry explained that this is an "expensive stone", but after speaking to management, they finally replaced it & sent it back in an acceptable time frame. I usually give people 5 stars & the stone is really fun & beautiful, but I felt like it was 3-4 star service.

product_title: Aiyaya Round Silver Zircon Sparkling Crystal Rings for Women Sz6
review_headline: Beautiful on my small, dainty finger
review_body:
This ring is beautiful and delicate on my tiny hand and finger. I am married and was surprised at how nice this ring looks for not being the real thing. I've been wearing this ring on my right hand and although there are some obvious differences, I'm quite impressed with the quality and beauty of this ring when placed side by side with my wedding ring.

For someone who cannot afford the real thing or may not be seriously ready for commitment yet, this ring is great. With the small price tag and beautiful design, this ring is perfect for someone who is just starting out. I've seen both solitaire bridal rings and rings that feature stones on the sides of a ring and know these are both popular designs. What I haven't seen before though is the design of this ring that includes both and I really like it.

product_title: King Will CLASSIC Men's 8MM Multi Faceted Tungsten Carbide Ring Polished Wedding Engagement Band
review_body:
This is one of those items that you'll find on Amazon with prices ranging from $0.99 to over $50, with list prices going into the hundreds. For what are probably identical pieces. For $0.99 you'll pay shipping and you won't get a product fulfilled by Amazon. So, you're on your own if you don't get what you expected.

King Will charges less than $20, which I was happy to pay to get the assurance I wouldn't be stuck with a piece of garbage. And I wasn't. It is exactly what I wanted and expected. The surface is that darker silver color you'd expect from tungsten carbide. The facets are cleanly cut and highly polished. It is a comfort fit design and the not overly domed, which is what I wanted. The edges of the ring are nice and thin; also what I wanted.

Would I have gotten the same thing for half the price? Maybe. But $19 is not a huge investment for an attractive wedding band and one that I won't likely be wearing on my wedding day.

So, I'm quite satisfied with this purchase, and have absolutely no complaints of the product or vendor.

review_body: My fiancé bought me this for my birthday (I picked it out lol) and I couldn't be happier with it. I'm obsessed with rose gold and am always looking for rose gold jewelry. This necklace has become my go to necklace because it's beautiful and versatile. You can wear it for an everyday look by pairing it with a nice pair of Rose gold hoops or you can dress it up by wearing it with fancier earrings (my fiancé also picked out-by himself-a pair of gorgeous Rose gold earrings with Swavorski crystals from another vendor). I didn't have anything with white sapphires but they're a wonderful alternative. I don't like cubic zirconia but diamonds are normally too pricey for him so the sapphires are perfect and look to me more like diamonds. It's the perfect size as well & unlike some other reviewers I think the chain is the perfect length. And the price is amazing! It definitely looks more pricey than it is. Seriously, if you're considering buying it for yourself (ladies) or buying as a gift (guys), don't hesitate. You will not be sorry!

product_title: Love Wish Pearl Kit Love Dolphins Pendant
review_body: Ordered two kits for my 10 and 11 year old nieces. They loved breaking open the oyster shell, digging out the pearl, and putting the necklace together.  The pearls were both odd shaped and the same color; probably fake but do kids really care?  My nieces didn't seem to suspect.  The oyster shells were extremely difficult to get apart (needed a flat head screwdriver instead of the little plastic spatula that came in the kit), so I suspect the shells were glued shut.  The necklace pendant was of decent quality for kids jewelry.  It exceeded my expectations, given the cheap price.  I opened and drained the water from the little cans that held the oyster, and the rest of the process of the girls getting the pearl out was minimally messy.

review_body: I previously wrote a review but It is no longer able to be seen, my opinion has not changed, I first received this item and it was just plain, no design or accents at all. the company contacted me, because they wanted to make it right. I was very pleased with that. I sent the item back in extremely excited. When the item was returned to me. 1 of the earrings were perfect and so pretty. the other has some sort of rainbow thing going on. I really wanted a refund at that point since I was just tired of dealing with it. I was made aware by the seller they do not give refunds, they was asked did I look at it in the daylight, that really angered me. What a question to ask. and then I was told to rub it with a soft dry cloth. and of course I did, NO it did not change anything. so how am I supposed to wear these earring. hmmm I guess I cant. The person at the company also says that he inspected them himself to make sure they were right. well I cant believe that. and would either be impossible or you just didn't care...this has been the worst purchase I have ever made. So no I would not recommend this item to anyone. and I'm very grateful that it is unavailable for anyone else to purchase...please learn from my mistake.

product_title: European Charm Beaded Bracelet Mom for Women and Teen Girls 7.5 Inch Professional Quality
review_headline: The perfect gift for the mom in your life
review_body:
Ok, so Mother's Day has come and gone but how many times a year can you think of to get MOM a gift that's beautiful and will make her swoon? I think any day of the year is suitable. If I still had a mom, I wouldn't need a particular day to gift her something that says I love you and you're special.

This bracelet is really gorgeous and has an elegance that a mother can pull off with her pajamas on because she's been too busy making everyone else breakfast and lunches to go to bother getting ready herself.

I love the shiny sparkly that this has, it's not over the top and it's perfectly understated with still having the Pow to catch the eyes of the beholder.

Best part is? If there's something that she loves (other than you) you can add a charm of it! Does she love to collect anything in particular? Add a bead... There's so many options that you have, and you know that she will appreciate any gesture like this. It's a great gift for the MOM in your life... I remember when I had gotten something like this for mine, and I remember how happy she was. You know those happy mom tears? You'll get that.

I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do the review on my own.

review_body:
This is a review of the blue & silver single link motorcycle chain bracelet. This is one weighty piece of jewelry though it doesn't feel too heavy on the wrist when you're wearing it. The blue is somewhere between navy and cobalt with subtle tones of dark purple. The bracelet is a little darker than the images on Amazon portray but this is still a very handsome bracelet. product_title: Starfish Lip Ring BioPlastic Labret Stud 18g-16g-14g Tragus-Helix-Flat Back Cartilage Earring
review_headline: The picture makes the ring look much better than it actually is
review_body: The picture makes the ring look much better than it actually is. The star basically looks like this an asktrice [ *], and the silicon looking spacer holding the star ring in place is actually more like a clear Capri sun straw that's been melted at one end when you see it in person. The ring and the space barely fit into each other. Basically, you have to shove this hard, sharp, jagged piece of plastic in your piercing from behind, without the rough plastic in the earing tearing the piercing space and causing bleeding, then you place the metal "starfish" into the plastic hole, like pushing a thumbtack into a plastic straw but through your piercing space. I gave this a 5 star rating so that others will read this and hopefully not buy.

product_title: Stud Earrings, Birth Stone Color Cubic Zirconia Safety Back Ear Studs Made for Kids Earrings 5mm Stone
review_headline: Daughter loves these earrings and hasn't lost them yet!
review_body:
My oldest daughter, who is 5 years old, recently got her ears pierced. The earrings she got them pierced with were stainless steel. I am allergic to nickle, and with hers only being done a month I was afraid to put cheap earrings in her ears when I could change them.

I ended up having to change them before her 6 weeks was up due to issues with the piercing earrings. I gave up and let her wear cheap earrings which she lost two pair of along with a pair of my gold and real stone ones. This is when I came across these amazing earrings. They have a screw on back!!!

These earrings are not only gorgeous, but the stone being 5mm fits nicely on her ear. For now she wanted the pink ones so we started there. She has been wearing these about 2 weeks now with no issues! They haven't once come loose or fell out.

They are very simple to screw together once in her ear. My only complaint is the bar that goes in ear seems to be a little bit thicker than a normal earring. Almost like it is gauged somewhat. I was afraid to put them in her newly pierced ears at first, but my husband said they looked like the smallest gauge possible. They did take a little more work getting in her ear, but after that it's been problem free.

Overall I would definitely say these are kid friendly earrings. The price seemed a little high for one pair, but being stainless steel and screw back means no allergic reactions and harder to lose! So in the end the price has been worth every penny so far and I'm sure I will be buying her more for presents later! Plus they come in adorable little gift box.

I would recommend these earrings to anyone looking for a quality earring that is hard to loose! Just be careful when you first put them through as they do seem thicker.

review_headline: Not Sure I Believe it is 925 Sterling Silver
review_body: This is a nice ring. The abalone had bright, beautiful colors and the design was unique. I purchased it as a gift chiefly because it was an djustable abalone ring. It is stamped "925" on the inside but when I pulled it out of the box and tried to give it a little force to adjust it (not Hulk force, just expecting a little struggle), it moved apart quickly and without much resistance like a cheap ring made of pot metal you would give to a child. My concern is that if it gets caught on something while being worn, since it is an open ring, it will give way and fall off, possibly becoming lost. I doubt it is actually 92.5% sterling silver based upon this malleability.

product_title: Stainless Steel 4 Round Clear Cubic Zirconia Stone Anniversary Wedding Band Ring
review_headline: Good ring, nice metal, ok setting.
review_body:
Good ring and sturdy stainless steel construction. I got this ring to go with my stainless steel 4mm wedding band. It looks very nice paired with this ring. The stones are not huge, nor are they over the top sparkly, so it is a believable piece.

The setting of the stones is not overly impressive. The stones seem to be firmly set, but not uniformly set. This was fairly obvious to me right away, but I am fairly picky. Also, two of the outer prongs are kind of rough or sharp, so those might catch on delicate fabric or hair. I have not had a problem so far, but it's only been a day. One thing I do like is the low profile style. The stones are low on the hand, so the ring is very comfortable and fits well next to the band.

I would recommend this ring as a purchase for yourself as an addition to your wedding ring wardrobe or as a right hand ring, but perhaps not as a gift unless you have it shipped to you and inspect it yourself first.

The best part of this purchase is lower cost, quick shipping, and synthetic stones (not a fan of the diamond trade).

review_body: My wife wears these now and then.  They look great under a T-shirt or sheer blouse, as her "high beams" stay on constantly.  She says she can only stand them for an hour or two without having sex, which makes it even nicer when I see she's wearing them!  Ladies, to use, get your nipples erect, pull the teat out a little bit and slip it on.  They stay on pretty well, but a bit of appropriate body adhesive would help.  Women with small nipples or men might find these fall off too easily without adhesive.

product_title: Aiyaya Round Silver Zircon Sparkling Rings for Women Sz9
review_body:
This ring is gorgeous! It is actually a lot nicer than I was expecting it to be. This would be the perfect ring for someone who has an expensive diamond but can't wear it every day to work because of worry of damage or policies at their employer. They could still show they were married or engaged in a stylish way but not be worried about losing or damaging a super expensive ring.
I am really impressed with the detail of the ring. The band has intricately carved details that really stand out. The channel set "diamonds" really look great and are set in very well (and perfectly even) and the center stone has a great sparkle to it. It might be even more sparkly than some people's real diamond rings!
After wearing it for several days as a right hand ring, I find it to be extremely comfortable. It runs true to size and does not cause any discomfort or discoloration to my skin from wearing it. I also got several compliments on my new ring. I was happy to sing its praises.
I received this product at a discounted price in exchange for my honest and unbiased opinion and review.

product_title: Qalo Men's Pick Axe Quality Q2X Silicone Ring, Black, Size 11
review_headline: You will look goth, techno and sporty in this ring, and some people may even think you look stylish.
review_body:
So you spent some serious money on your real ring? Probably you did, and now you are off to Rio, where you are scared of being mugged, kidnapped or worse, and that darn Cartier ring of yours will be the first thing they pull off of your corpse. Now wouldn't that wreck anyone's trip? Or, if you are lucky, and nothing bad happens down there along these lines, you might feel compelled to go body surfing at Ipanema ,and there you could easily lose your ring in the ocean. Or, you might have a gym at your hotel, and if you decide that you want to revitalize your biceps with some curls, you could pinch your finger against that nice ring of yours, and potentially bend it too. And there are other frightful things that could go wrong with your real ring, some which I am unable to mention, and that is why you should buy this ring.

I must admit, it is a bit expensive for what it is. It looks good, but is little more than a fancy rubber band, so I was a little surprised by the price. But hey -- it represents the mystical union of you and your beloved, so go for it and don't be so cheap. And get one for her, for crying out loud.

But now we come the the only real problem -- the sizing. You may think you are genius for knowing your ring size, or you might think of yourself as resourceful when you download a ring-sizing guide, but none of this matters. Why? Because this is a stretchy ring. It is not rigid, so you MUST order it small. I had to send my first one back because of this. Sure, it might slide on easily, and then you may think you got just the right size, but you would be wrong. When you get into the pool, or even when you sweat a lot, this ring can slip off your finger quite easily -- it will do this when washing your hands too. So BUY SMALL. How small? I don't know! Two sizes? Remember, when you are cold, it will come off that much easier, so that too must be considered.
Bottom line -- I dig this ring, but you should probably go to where they have them as opposed to ordering online, and you should try it on. Otherwise you will have to return it.d to ordering online, and you should try it on. Otherwise you will have to return it.

review_headline: This is an incredibly beautiful jewelry set
review_body: This is an incredibly beautiful jewelry set! The set itself was packaged very well which is always appreciated and makes it perfect for gifting. The necklace was set against a card and the earrings were in a separate baggie with an anti-tarnish paper tab, and both pieces were packaged nicely in a little box with a cushion. The set also came with a cute little organza bag to either store the jewelry in or to place the jewelry in for gifting. The stones are nice and clear and very shiny. The chain is a perfect standard length. It is a nice, light chain but also quite durable. The clasp is easy to open and to close. The earrings complement the necklace perfectly and have a nice hinge closure back that is easy to use. They feel comfortable in my ears and look beautiful! The rose coloring is just lovely, and I really love the look of the whole set. It's a great set that is great quality and so beautiful to wear. I received this item at a discount in exchange for my honest review.

product_title: Unistyle Mens Stainless Steel Necklace Blue Lords Prayer Cross Pendant with 18.5" Chain
review_headline: A  perfect way to display your faith
review_body: This cross makes a great gift for something like a Confirmation or a First Holy Communion.  It allows the wearer to display their faith in a stylish way without being too in your face.  I really like the way that The Lord's Prayer is etched into the cross.  It is small print but the print is still large enough that you can read the words.  And at the center of all the words is another cross.  I like the subtle addition of the second cross  The cross is a nice size.  You can easily wear it outside to put your faith on display or wear it under a shirt without it being obtrusive.  The chain has a nice manly look to it with just the right amount of shine.  It is easy to get on and off with a convenient lobster clasp.  Even though it is a larger jewelry item, it is light weight and comfortable enough to wear every day.  I really like this cross and highly  recommend it to anyone looking for a unique cross.

product_title: Real Bullet Necklace Punk Silver Black Metal Rock Death
review_body:
Love it! Haven't had a bullet necklace in awhile. The last one I had (a completely different necklace and bullet mind you) came off the chain while at a club (hah). This is not a dainty or feminine necklace in any way. I like layering and balancing out it's badassness with more feminine looking pieces.
The chain is really thick and is also much longer than the chain in the photo. At least, the chain that came with the one I received is. It hangs just below the breast bone. Actually, I like the length a lot, tbh. Allows for more layering options.
Honestly, this bullet necklace can't be beat for the price. Quality wise it looks like it should cost at least 3x as much, so I'm pretty happy. Has a really nice weight to it but isn't uncomfortably heavy.
The bullet I received is in perfect condition, no dents or scratches and is really shiny. Really great option for those who like to mix looks like I do, want to add a bit of rocker/punk/hardcore/gothness to their accessories, or for those that just prefer more masculine jewelry.
Very pleased!

product_title: Unistyle Classic Stainless Steel Key Pendant Necklace 22"
review_body:
Lets start with the positives:
When you receive the pendant it is packaged in a nice box and is tied down so that you don't have to worry about the chain and pendant getting tangled up within itself.
The pendant itself is decently made, its sturdy and doesnt seem that it will bend easy or break.
It is heavy in terms of a normal necklace pendant, but since it is a "key" it feels more real.
It came nice and polished so it is nice and shiny. It is large enough to be noticed from a distance.
Now the negatives;
It did not come on a chain like pictured in the default stock photo, it came on a ball chain similar to those on cheap dog tags and key-chains. It is a shorter chain so it is uncomfortable to wear. Though on my son it seems to be a good length.
The "staining" on the key is very poor quality. It looks like it is just black glue or something that they connected the fob to the "key" part.

All in all it is a decent necklace

I received this necklace at a promotional rate to provide my honest review.

product_title: Handmade Jewelry Green Illusion Necklace Earring Jewelry Set for Women
review_body:
This necklace and earrings are absolutely gorgeous! When you first receive it, it is packaged in this gorgeous Tiffany blue box and the earrings are in one organza bag and the necklace is packaged in another. The presentation is lovely.
The necklace and earrings are made with gorgeous light green beads/stones and they are very flattering to every skin tone.
The necklace has the chain that allows you to set it to different lengths depending on what you would like to do. I put the chain on the last link and it was long enough to be below my collarbone, and the tightest was almost near a choker length.
The earrings are on a hook/dangle and do not come with backings for them, but I did not have any problems with them sliding out or moving at all while wearing them.
I think you will be very pleased with these homemade necklace and earrings and I recommend you add them to your jewelry collection. You will be pleasantly surprised.

I received this at a promotional rate to provide my honest review

review_headline: I love this braided leather bracelet.
review_body:
I love this Blue Braided Genuine Leather men's Bracelet by YiuYiuMa. I love almost all the jewelry from YiuYiuMa New York, they are well made, stylish, modern looking, and very up to date with current fashion trend. Also they are very affordable, but the price doesn't comprise the quality, Plus they are from my city New York City, i love that fact and i like to promote local brands which are loyal to the communities they work in.

This blue men's bracelet is made with high quality leather and tightly braided to give it a neat clean look.The bracelet has a steel clasp to open/close.You have the press the button down for the bracelet to open and it snaps back in for secure closing.The clasp is made from stainless steel and polished very nicely.I love the fact that on the clasp there is fine checker locking design.The bracelet color/looks was exactly as pictured and the quality is exceptional.

Leather bracelet size: 8 1/4 inches L x 0.20 inches W . It is prefect size. I love that its not too loose nor too tight.

Now for packaging and shipping: The bracelet was packed nicely in a bubble warp and was put in a small red velvet pouch.The shipping was also very fast.I got the bracelet within two days after placing the order online.Lucky i bought this at a discounted price for my unbiased review. I am so glad that i did. Its a great quality, durable and luxurious looking bracelet.I highly recommend this braided bracelet by YiuYiuMa.Below are few pictures of the bracelet that i took.

product_title: European Charm Beaded Bracelet Pink Vintage Cancer Awareness for Women Teen Girls 7.5 Inch, Prime Quality
review_headline: Like pink and shiny and beautiful?!! Then this is for you!
review_body:
This bracelet is really adorable, and I am going to probably have a difficult time expressing my ridiculous amount of love for it.

My best friend in the whole world is currently recovering from breast cancer, so this time actually means a lot to me. Even though I'm not the one who went through the cancer, I have been there to hold her hand throughout the whole thing. And it was a rough ride for her, so I'm probably going to give that charm to her because she definitely earned it. It's very detailed, and beautiful. I think that's the perfect gift.

There are a couple of other charms on here that scream out my name, take for instance the little money charms. I show them to my husband and he started laughing asking me if I was going to spend those also. No, I'm not. Those are just gonna go on my personal charm bracelet!

And then we have the oh my gosh absolutely adorable, for the purpose of this review, iced tea charm. Whether it's a Long Island, or regular tea, doesn't matter. That's screaming out my name 1 million times.

And, my favorite color in the whole wide world is pink! I just love this one. The super cute and adorable oh my gosh music charm is perfect. I know someone who is in the music industry that is definitely going to have a charm put on their bracelet! OK, so there's really nothing that I hate about this charm bracelet except for the fact that I need to make four different ones out of this. I bought these for my daughter as she loves rainbows (and unicorns....). Anyway - the ONLY reason I purchased this specific product is because it was supposed to be made out of stainless steel. I personally have a reaction to anything other than steel, platinum and gold so I didn't want to take chances with my daughter. Long story short, this product is pretty BUT definitely not made of steel (or perhaps it's plated with some other material, who knows).
After putting them in, her ears turned beat red and within two days her entire ear lobe was discolored in this blackish/greenish hue which I usually get when I am wearing fake jewelry. This is false advertisement so just for the blatant lie I'll give this product a pretty sad 1 star rating.

They are nicely packaged and include a very nice velvet bag. This set also include a Certificate of Authenticity and care instructions to help you maintain and take proper care of the earrings. The setting of the stone, color of metals, are really good and give it a high quality appeal. I really like the single stone, it's simple and elegant. I'm really happy with this set, my personal favorite of the two is the silver set, but the gold one is just as beautiful. I recommend this set to any one looking to add a classic, simple touch to their everyday look at a very reasonable price. I received this product at a discounted rate in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

review_body:
I had to straighten and rebend them because they stuck out. I suppose that is to be expected because everyone's nose is different. But i doubt very many people have a thick enough nostril to use it the way it is.
The stainless steel is darker and less shiny than I was hoping for. I guess I've never had a bezel set nose stud before, I didn't realise how much of the dark steel would show when I'm wearing it.
Those things are annoying, but my biggest issue is that the stones fall out after a day or two. I take out the stud while I'm getting ready for bed so I can exfoliate my face. In the morning, I put it back in after I put on my makeup. So it's not getting snagged on blankets or anything.
I guess I'm still looking for the perfect nose stud.

review_headline: Just as described and looks great.
review_body:
I really love this bracelet combo!! It's a bit big on me since i am a women's wrist. It does not fit my husband. These are made for Asian sizing (which are smaller if you are buying from the US). I found this out with shirts once. I'm a M in the USA, but a L or XL in Asian sizing. *sniff* so sad, but thats the way the cookie crumbles.

Even on the last notches it's still loose. Very happy with it. Looks cool & Steampunk. On the smaller bracelet it has a small long cross & rectangular plate. There is writing: "I feel about you/ makes my heart/lone to be free". But I sautered on some gears over it. It comes in a red box and on a simple paper filled pillow cushion. Great to help keep form.

I already get complements from friends & strangers. The images are only of how it looked when I opened the box right away. Not my modifications.

The only draw back is getting them on are bit difficult. Not really hard, but not as easy as most bracelets.

Still I would buy again. It was through Prime, so shipping went smoothly.

product_title: Aiyaya Round 1010mm CZ Ring with Engagement for Women Wedding
review_headline: My Wife Got 3 Separate Compliments On This Ring While Out To Dinner This Evening!!!
review_body: I got this ring as another gift for my wife. It's the 4th time I have done business with Aiyaya and there is a reason that I keep coming back. My wife loved this gift just as much as the other ones I have recently given her. This review is a reflection of her opinion and comments regarding the ring. This ring is comfortable on the finger. She instantly commented on how unique the cathedral setting and the channel set stones climbing up towards the main stone was. The channel set stones are very small and delicate looking which makes the main stone all the more stunning. The ring is plated in 18K gold and shines very well. You can actually see your reflection in the metal! The main cubic zirconia stone is beyond breathtaking. It's cut in such a way that it reflects light from so many angles. When you look down into the center of the stone you will see what I mean. It looks like a gemological kaleidoscope. I took my wife out to dinner at a local Italian restaurant this evening. In the dimmed lights of the restaurant that ring attracted a lot of attention. The ring isn't subtle. Two waitresses and a patron complimented her on it. You know, I never understood why a ring has to be naturally mined in order for people to want it, because this ring is definitely beautiful. It doesn't matter whether the stones were created. If you are looking to give the special woman in your life something that expresses the magnitude of your esteem and affection for her then this would be a wonderful choice. I can't wait for the next opportunity to purchase from Aiyaya. They make such beautiful jewelry and this was no exception! My wife has no problem telling me when she doesn't like something so I am confident in recommending this product to others.  I was provided this product at a discounted price in exchange for an honest unbiased evaluation.

product_title: Fashion Ring the Lord of the Rings Couple Jewelry Stainless Steel Wedding Ring
review_headline: A Different Look for LOTR Fans
review_body: This ring is beautiful. The black is a pure, shiny black, not dull, flat, or clouded.  The etching stands out nicely against the dark band, inside and out, but looks a little more like white, rather than silver.  Fits true to size. The inside of the ring has a slight convex angle to it rather than flat.  The edge is a little thin, which gives it a sharp feel on that tender skin between your fingers.  I was hoping it would be more of a 'comfort' edge like the LOTR ring I bought this to replace.  I like the black though so I will keep and wear it, with luck I will get used to the edge with use.  Can't beat the price so I am happy with this purchase. Update:  Have been wearing this ring daily since I received it and it has really stood up to the challenge.  It has been banged, bumped, and exposed to various harsh chemicals and has held up pretty well.  So far it has only two small dings near the edge and a few hard to see, superficial scratches.  At this point I would say it seems fairly durable.

product_title: DTLA Phoenix Wrap Around Design Sterling Silver Ring Oxidized
review_headline: Good design; a few things to consider
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:74b0ca5415975a3ae4134796e9ce57a1]] I love the design of this ring. I've had it for about a month now and wear it fairly often. It has held up well so far and has had no tarnishing or other issues. My only complaint is that it turns my finger green when I wear it for too long, but that problem is easily fixed with nail polish.

The sizes for this ring seem to run a little large. I ordered a size 6, and the ring that came was more like a size 7. Size 7 still fits on my finger, so it wasn't an issue for me. But I would suggest ordering a size smaller than what you normally wear.

I also wanted to point out that the ring appears to be upside down in the picture the seller has posted. The design looks better if you flip it over (I couldn't figure out how to add a picture to the review, so I've added a short video of the ring facing the other way). Also, the 925 marking on the inside of the ring is upside down when the ring is held the way the seller shows it in the picture.

product_title: Sterling Silver Simulated Diamond Checkered Ring (Size 5 - 9)
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:7f2f22641e9019e7659091bc8552f12f]] Very pretty ring, and a real statement piece, especially on larger hands.

The thing I really like about this ring is that although it is wide, it's quite comfortable because the back is more narrow and unadorned.

Because of the way that the stones are set, and also the size of the stones, you get more of an understated sparkle. When traveling, it's not always the best idea to wear your real diamonds, this is a way to get the look without the high price and risk.

It comes with a presentation box, perfect for storing your ring or when you are giving it as a gift.

product_title: Bling Jewelry CZ Cursive Alphabet Letter P Pendant Rhodium Plated Necklace 16 Inches
review_headline: Awesome buy for the money, Solid quality pendant.
review_body:
This was a really good purchase. There aren't a lot of good options for script font pendants and this was the best I could find. I was unsure at first because of the low price, but I figured I'd give it a shot since its only $30. For that price, you can't go wrong. The pendant actually includes a good amount of metal work and has solid weight to it. It doesn't feel cheap or look like costume jewelry. The necklace that comes with it is pretty thin and dainty, but I was only interested in the pendant anyway. If you are looking for a nice script letter pendant, check out this line from BlingJewelry.com.

As a side note, I ordered mine through blingjewelry.com because they have an option to have the necklace come in a nice jewelry box for an extra few dollars. I don't think you get that option on amazon, but I could be wrong.

Also, I would love to see a pendant like this available in 14K white gold with real diamond chips. I couldn't find anything close enough to this design online anywhere.

review_body: This bracelet is very pretty but I did not expect it to be so stiff.  It's not a fluid bracelet like I thought, it's more like a delicate bangle with a clasp.  It does sparkle and shine in the light and has very pretty detail, I also like the 7" length for more slender wrists and the fact that it is coated against tarnish.  I purchased this as a gift for my future daughter in law and hope she likes it, my only concern is that it might kink if not taken care of and stored properly.  Shipping was super quick but it came in a plastic bag in a plain box with cotton and a red pouch which does not do it justice.  I ended up repackaging it outside of the plastic bag in a nicer box with a dark background that lends itself to the shiny detail much better than cotton in a box.  It looks more expensive and elegant up against a dark backdrop.  Other than that, it is a very pretty bracelet.  Only time will tell how it holds up.

product_title: Titanium 4MM High Polish Plain Dome Wedding Band Ring (Sizes 6 to 13.5)
review_body: I needed a larger ring after surgery on ring finger. I am using this one as an alternate, until I eventually get my original gold ring re-sized.  Nice and shiny out of the box, but finish has turned to a more brushed metal look after a couple of weeks which is just fine for me (married over  25 years).  I also have been doing a lot of lot of construction and landscaping projects around home since receiving this ring, so that likely has accelerated the finish wear,  so your experience will likely vary from mine.  Overall, I really like the ring. It is very inexpensive, looks nice and feels good on the hand. Remember the ring is a symbol of a relationship, not the value of it. Precious metals are nice, but this ring is a great value as an alternate, replacement, or even a primary ring.

product_title: Diaura Sterling Silver Square Shape Diamond Stud Earrings
review_headline: Understated Bling & Sparkle, Daytime to Evening, I Like These Earrings
review_body:
I like the earrings. They give enough "bling" and "sparkle" to accent with quiet sophistication. They could work well with a business to evening outfit. I like the way the diamonds catch the light and I'm a silver jewelry person so these are a good fit for me.

The earrings come in a nice black box suitable for gifting, but a bit on the large side to keep them. If you looking at these for a gift this may be a plus.

The posts are surgical steel and do not irritate my ears the way a number of my French hook hearings can after wearing them for a day. The backs are simple metal spring clasps. Mine have stayed on fine all day which is good for me.

I like these diamond studs. They are great for a day to evening accessory with an understated touch. I heard if you really want to get someone's attention, whisper. These stud earrings are like visual equivalent to a party whisper. Excellent!

Hope this helps someone!

product_title: European Charm Beaded Bracelet Tree of Life Green for Women and Teen Girls 8.5 Inch, Prime Quality
review_headline: Such a beautiful and meaningful bracelet.
review_body: There are so many different interpretations about what the tree of life stands for. I actually have made it a habit of giving The Tree of Life pendants or bracelets, or paintings to my friends who have recently had kids. I like to think that it represents your family.  This one is definitely no exception. It's beautiful in the detail, and the dangle on the tree of life charm is perfect. It's not too long, and it won't get caught on things because it's smooth and flush.  The other charms on this bracelet are magnificent, i love the two leaf charms, and the two flower charms. They all go together with the tree of life, and the two glass charms that have the glitter and flowers in them are magnificent.  This comes in a 7 & a half inch bracelet, but you can extend it. The snake chain has an easy open class, so you don't have to ask anyone for help to put it on or take it off.  This bracelet is the perfect amount of class and elegance, and even the two beads that have the crystals in it that give it the shine go perfectly with the rest of the bracelet. It's an eye catching piece, and you will not be sorry if you purchase this.  I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do the review on my own.

review_body:
[[ASIN:B00Q7EO7NO 10k Yellow Gold Heart & Cross Pendant with an 18 Inch Gold Layered Figaro Necklace]]
I purchased this cross for someone I love, consider family and have known for 55 years. I had thought about making this purchase for a while, but had not seen anything I felt would reflect her spirituality, as well as her own personal taste; this looked like it might do both. Although the pictures showed that this cross has diamonds, the description didn't mention them. I decided to buy it anyway. It was an excellent choice! The cross is beautiful, it does have diamonds as shown and they are clear with sparkle. The Figaro chain is lovely and a perfect match for this cross. I was not expecting the cross to be this beautiful, but it is, and it comes in a small, gold gift box. I completely agree with the others who have given this cross 5 stars.

review_body:
I received this charm at a discount in exchange for an honest review.

If you look closely at my picture, you can tell the "i" is very faded. Other than that, I love this charm, and I love the fact that it has Special Friend written on both sides. I also love the fact that the charm is a dangling charm and not a charm that has two holes in it. It fits perfectly into my snake chain charm bracelet!

I recommend this charm to anyone who wants a charm bracelet or anyone looking to fill their charm bracelet with meaningful charms!

Thank you for choosing me to receive this charm!

product_title: 14k Yellow Gold Ball Stud Earrings pushback 3 4 5 6 7 8 10 12 14 MM
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:66915b74af4966bfb8204b95e96f9afc]] Beautiful earrings. Very comfortable on! Feels as if you're not wearing earrings. I slept in them and they didn't feel uncomfortable or hurt. The post is shorter than most post earrings, which is great for children. Due to the short post, when the back is attached when wearing, you won't feel the post, but I still get a good secure fit without being tight on my adult ear lobes. Very comfortable! The backs are small as well, discreet, and tight. I showered in them and haven't had any discoloration or peeling. And the gold is very smooth and looks high quality.

UPDATE:
November 10, 2016
I've been wearing these almost every single day since reviewing them since I don't like big jewelry or any jewelry that isn't "real" (I can't afford diamonds yet hahaha ). I take them out maybe once a week just to clean my ears better and gently wipe them off. I don't use jewelry cleaner on them, just a Q- tip or tissue with a little water. I still sleep in them, shower in them and no gold is flaking, no scratches, and no dents in the ball. I'm pretty gentle on my jewelry though. I have lost a earring about 3 times, and by the grace of my nephews and their young eyes, they found them each time. Point is, make sure you check them every now and then. I think mines just get loose because I never take them out (besides once a week) and with doing my hair/ sleeping they will naturally loosen up. The backs are still pretty snug when on all the way. Lastly, I've never experienced any irritation or them hurting due to the length.

*Sample provided in exchange for my 100% honest review

product_title: OKAJEWELRY Leaves Ear Cuffs and Wrap Earring No Pierced Gold Tone
review_headline: Received LOTS of compliments! Highly recommended!!
review_body:
I love the heck out of this new little Ear Cuff! I wore it to work today (a day after I received it in the mail) and I got lots of compliments at work! Customers stopped me and told me how much they loved my ear cuff, and asked where I got it from. Three of the other workers also stopped and asked where I had bought my Ear Cuff and where they could purchase a similar one! Everyone absolutely loved it. It draws attention without being "too much." It's the perfect accessory to any outfit (especially black and white - which is what I wore - so it definitely drew a lot of attention). I also have long hair, so I was worried about it getting caught in my hair. But that didn't happen at all! It actually helped keep some of my hair out of my face so that was a plus. I'll definitely be wearing it a lot more. Recommended highly to anyone who enjoys wearing "statement" pieces, especially in unexpected places - like your ear!

I received this product at a discount for my honest and unbiased feedback.

product_title: Lukso :Indian Jewelry Set Resins Geometric Pendants Vintage Silver Metal Chokers Necklaces Earrings Sets
review_body: I really like this type of Native American/South American jewelry, and I find this to be a very attractive piece. It did make me break out on my upper chest because it is not sterling silver, but the seller does not claim that it is, and it would be more expensive if it was. The earrings and necklace can be worn together or apart, and I am very very happy with it. Exactly what I was looking for. The only improvement would be if it were sterling silver, and that would be more expensive. I have very sensitive skin, and do tend to break out on that spot, so many people could probably wear this without getting a rash. I like the heaviness of the piece; it does not feel heavy, but if you want that kind of look, that's it. Very nice!

***Update***

The last time I had them on I spilled coffee on myself and had to take a quick shower and did not remove them - the rose gold completely came off and what is left is a dirty copper looking metal.

****************************************************************

product_title: Teacher Prayer Silver Tone Bangle Bracelet with Dangling Apple Charm
review_headline: Pretty but potentially dangerous with warning label
review_body:
Purchased two of these for end-of-year Thank You/Goodbye gifts given to my kid's PS and 1st grade teacher's. They seemed to like them very much, wearing them up until the very last moments kids were in respective classes, with many words of appreciation and comments on how pretty they were.
However, I was a bit taken back upon reading the warning inside the gift box, on the plastic wrap packaging which presumably keeps the bracelet from getting scuffed, it says something along the lines of: Warning: Not to be worn by anyone 12 years of age or younger. I can't quote it verbatim, since it's been several months now since I gave these as gifts, but to me that says there is likely some mercury and/or some other harmful variety of metals.
I had reservations once reading this, but seeing how I had purchased the bracelets in March, with school year end being May/June, and nothing else in mind to give as my appreciation for all their dedication, I gave them to each teacher. Concerns over health of a young child who might encounter the item unattended at teacher's home or even in the classroom still do consume me. Not to mention, who says that such harmful anomalies are only harmful to the young? I am aware of affects of metals like mercury and their harmful attributes to the developing brain and body, but seriously, I'm of the thought that if it's bad for one human it's likely bad for all. Possibly should be more description with regards to this item, or any sold to the general public here on Amazon, which definitely include information about warnings and harmful substances that are possibly contained in any items for sale.

product_title: Ivation IVUC96 Digital Ultrasonic Cleaner with Adjustable Power, Removable 17-ounce Stainless Steel Wide Tank, Jewelry Basket, Watch & Earring Holder, CD DVD Stand, 5 Individual Cleaning Cycles & Auto-Shut-off - Generates 42,000 Ultra Sonic Energy Waves Per Second
review_headline: It's attractive & the removable basin with a handle makes it super easy to fill & empty & clean
review_body: This ultrasonic cleaner is actually much nicer than I expected. It's attractive & the removable basin with a handle makes it super easy to fill & empty & clean. I have not found it to be able to get things sparkling brand new squeaky clean, but it does get them much cleaner than anything other than tediously hand-scrubbing them would. I'm still sort of experimenting with the things I can put into it. I'd also like to note that this device has well written directions, which is something I find often lacking with electronics, particularly unusual ones, that I've bought over the last several years. If I could change one thing about it, I'd allow the user to input cycle lengths longer than 480 seconds; it's not a huge deal, but I have something I need to clean for about 15 minutes at a time and so I have to stay at the ready with this to put it through a second cycle after the first finishes. The trade off with this, of course, is that the lack of a process for user fine tuning means it's dead simple to use and nearly impossible to screw up through user error. My purchase was from DBRoth and the item arrived brand new, with all internal components sealed in plastic inside an unblemished original product box.

review_body:
This is the coolest piece of jewelry that I have ever worn! It's so awesome in so many different ways. I really love how it has a bicycle chain design. I'm pretty sure it's not made out of an actual bicycle chain, because it's about 2-3 times wider than the chains on my bikes. So, it's really just inspired by bike chains, rather than that it's a real bike chain.

I also really like how heavy it is. It's a very thick, heavy bracelet, so it looks really manly. But, it's attractive enough, that my girlfriend would have taken it from me if it were more easy to adjust the size. It's 9" (the page says 8.86, but I measured it as 9). For me, it's a bit too big, since I have small wrists. I measured my wrists as 7", and I wish that the chain was 8", so I wish it were an inch smaller, and then it would fit me perfectly.

It's also made out of high quality stainless steel, so it looks great, and it'll keep looking great for years. I got the blue one, but I kind of wish I would have ordered the red one, because that one is awesome, too. I don't think you can go wrong with these great designs.

*LEADCIN gave me this chain to review*

product_title: Essential Oils Aromatherapy Diffuser Locket Necklace
review_body: Upon arrival, I immediately fell in love with this product!  The locket is beautiful, and looks exactly as pictured.  It is easy to open & close, and the clasp works well, holding the locket securely closed but not too difficult to open & close.  The chain is the perfect length for me.  I immediately filled it with my favorite essential oil blend and began wearing it daily.  I received many compliments on this necklace.  Unfortunately, though, after about a week of wearing it, the chain began to turn my neck green.  I'm not sure if the fact that I wear Essential Oils daily on my neck caused the chain coating to break down more quickly or what, but I was really disappointed.  I replaced the chain with a Sterling one and will continue to use the locket for now.  I can tell that the locket itself is beginning to discolor as well now, though.  Overall, I feel that this is a beautiful product and possibly a good entry point for someone wanting to try out wearing diffuser jewelry.  However, for an avid oil user like myself, I would recommend spending the extra money and purchasing sterling instead.

product_title: Sterling Silver Elongated Freshwater Cultured Pearl Framed Swarovski Zirconia Dangle Earrings
review_body:
These are nice earrings for the price. They're 925 sterling silver (stamped 925 on the back). They're pretty and very sparkly. Yes if you really look you can tell they're not real diamonds, but anything near this price has junk diamonds so I prefer the overly sparkly Swarovski crystals.

If they have any flaw it's that they're a little over-fancy. We don't have many dress up events in our year, and if we really had a need for dressy ear-rings, I think we'd buy something more expensive.

But overall, they have a lot of shine and sparkle and they look especially nice with a dark colored dress.

review_body: When I buy jewelry for myself it is usually something that I'm most often going to wear to work. Simple white pearls are the backbone of a classic professional wardrobe. With that said this is a very nice, well strung set of pearls. I have worn a strand that was a give for graduation from high school for a long time. They were a nice, graduated strand of medium quality pearls and I loved them for sentimental reasons. The quality, consistent coloring, weight, tight knots and dependable clasp will have me setting aside my sentimental favorites. These pearls will be worn at least weekly. Price wise, they are a good value. If they were any any less expensive, I would have been reluctant to order them.

product_title: European Bead Charm Bracelet for Women and Teen Girls Crown Vintage Made with Love 8.5 Inch Prime Quality
review_headline: It's  the best bracelet for me... I couldn't have picked a more suiting one!
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:dbbed0b0d208455b118493ecec55867a]]So I know what I am wearing today! As the ruler of my homestead, we will now refer to it as its own country, I do believe that I should be wearing a crown, which I really can't do on the top of my head due to it getting snagged constantly in my curls. So! The next best choice of course is going to be around my wrist. And I do believe that this is quite possibly the most perfect choice that is obtainable.

The crown that dangles on this is absolutely adorable and fitting for the current mood then I am in. Especially considering that I now declared my homestead its very own country and me the ruler. I digress. This has the super adorable dangle crown, and two other crowns on it. The heart charm that dangles next to the crown is also adorable, and it says made with love so I can be the queen of love. In my home anyway.

It has four of the red Murano lampwork clear glass charms, and they are really pretty. The red on those is exquisite. It has the silver color plated zinc alloy charms, and they have the red crystals going around them. They definitely pop. And then of course it has my crowns on it. I think I should have a bracelet that has nothing but crowns, but I don't want to go overboard.

The clasp is a barrel snap clasp so it's easy to put on yourself and take off, and the cute little pouch that it comes in makes it easy for gifting. This one is not going anywhere, ever! I'm just saying that if you wanted to gift something like this to someone that is easy. I am also going to send my husband this link, and hope he picks up on it.

Overall, I think that this bracelet is beautiful, stunning, definitely original, & I love the option of being able to take off the charms to add different ones because this is a universal type of bracelet, it will fit any of the other European style add a bead bracelet charms. I definitely need to look into getting more crowns. ;)

I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do the review on my own.to do the review on my own.

review_body:
Before I received this Tibetan prayer bracelet, I'll admit I was skeptical it would be as lovely as the product photo (nothing ever is). But when I took it out of the little cloth/burlap drawstring bag it comes in, I audibly oohed and ahhed. The product photo really is true to life. This is a beautiful, unusual and unique bracelet that I'm sure will get many compliments.

As far as overall quality goes, the elastic string is thick and seems fairly strong. The beads are all intact with no chipping or visible imperfections. So far I haven't had trouble with any of them breaking, but will update this review if they do.

The knot at the end is eye-catching and fun, but when I actually wear it, it tends to stick out a little and looks funny until I fiddle with it a bit to make it lie down flat. A minor issue, but one to be aware of.

The drawstring bag it comes in is cute, but cheaply made - not a big deal since I won't be wearing that around my wrist though!

I'm not Tibetan, Buddhist, nor do I use beads when I pray, but is a great colorful accessory that goes with almost anything I wear. It would also make a great gift.

I received a free sample of this product in exchange for testing, inspecting and reviewing it. I received no other compensation for my review and always give my honest and unbiased opinion of each product. I welcome your questions & comments on my experience.

product_title: JewelrieShop 20G Nose Ring Hoop Stainless Steel Nose Piercing Body Jewelry Set
review_body: I typically don't write reviews, but I want to put in a buyer beware so people don't have the same experience. I was so excited to get these rings that as soon as I got them, I disinfected the gold ring according to the instructions my piercer gave me (I got my nose done 5 months before I got these, so the piercing was healed, but I was still maintaining contact with my piercer since I wanted to get pierced by her again at some point) and I put it in. I had issues with getting it to stay in, but other than that, I was over the moon. I started to notice some irritation towards the end of the day, but I assumed that it was just from me having to readjust it more than my neometal stud. But when I woke up the next morning, I was in excruciating pain. My nose was swolen and I realized that it had to be from the ring since I had never had any problems before and, like I said, it was a healed piercing. So, I ran into the bathroom to change it and between the time that I took out the ring and went to re-insert the stud, my nose had already started to close up. I essentially ended up having to re-pierce my nose. Now, I'm not sure if there was something wrong with the metal used or if I might have a metal allergy (I have my ears pierced though and have never had any problem with sterling silver). My main point of this is BE CAREFUL. If you think you might have a metal allergy, don't get these. If you have a new piercing, don't get these. Just be cautious.

product_title: Jstyle Jewelry Stainless Steel Mens Chain Necklace for Men 3mm Wide 18-36 Inch
review_body:
I have been a fan of stainless steel jewelry for a while and I am happy to be adding this chain to my collection. It has a lovely high polish finish and a nice lobster clasp that is slightly larger than the ones found on fine jewelry, so it is easier to grasp. While it is listed as a men's chain, it is not that thick and could be worn by men or women tastefully.

A few things about stainless steel jewelry:

* It doesn't tarnish like silver
* It is low maintainance . No special storage, protection, cleaners or polishes required
* It is strong and won't break as easily as gold and silver
* It maintains it's finish and won't rust, turn green or turn black if you get it wet or sweat while wearing it
* It is inexpensive, but looks great
* It has a low incidence of metal allergies and sensitivities

Discounted sample provided for review.

review_body:
I just purchased this ring for my hubby to replace his old wedding band. It was 10kt yellow gold over sterling silver..and silly me for buying such bull..for my hubby...for our wedding, OMG!?!?!?!?
I don't know much about this stuff but, i guess i can say a lil' something about sterling silver being that i have a few rings of my own. I know that 1- They are very inexpensive, and 2- Will last a while if taken care of. I'v read a lot of reviews about this ring losing it's shine but I cant recall anyone trying to RESTORE THE SHING. Well, i'v read somewhere not too but i do it anyway. I wipe my rings down with a jewelry rag. I promise u will see a SHOWCASE SHINE!!
With that being said, i feel like this ring would be a good buy. I'm always prepared for sterling. I can't belive i let my sissy talk me into buying that other crap. I haven't gotten the ring but as soon as it comes..and if these settings allow me to revise or update what i have written here..i will be sure to tell u what were experiencing with it!

product_title: 2pcs 20g Gold & Silver Plated Nose Ring Piercing Hoop 20 Gauge 5/16"
review_headline: Silver ring is not really worth it-but if you like gold you'll be alright.
review_body:
I bought this since I really wanted a silver ring and was hoping to only use the gold one as a back up since I don't like gold that much. I do, however, have both good and bad news for both rings;
Silver- Magnet was very weak and it could stay on for more than two seconds. Five if you're lucky. In order to wear it, (which I do NOT recommend-forgive me I was stupid) I had to use smelly nail glue to glue the silver one on the outer side of my nose. (It didn't hurt at all only made a mark when the ring was removed and the glue would irritate my eyes.) Unfortunately, one day the glue dried out and I was hoping the silver ring would last a whole day without applying another coat-which it didn't and fell out on me. I was at school and didn't feel like crawling on the ground for a tiny piece of silver without standing out.
Gold- Stays in very well, does not need glue or anything to help keep it in. It sometimes will droop down so you might have to adjust it when wearing it. It also can be itchy sometimes if you're sensitive to gold. If you're allergic to gold, like my mom is, I'd steer clear.
If you prefer silver like me, don't buy these, you'll be stuck with gold.

review_headline: Wear it daily!  But the color is "off"...
review_body:
I withheld a star because for some reason the silver looks more like stainless steel than sterling silver...It's darker than the almost white I expect from the new gleam of sterling silver. So I can't wear it directly adjacent to most of my silver, except for some of the antique pieces.

I was gonna re-read the info on the site to make sure I didn't somehow scramble a piece of stainless into my meticulous sterling search but no, it's stamped 925. And I avoid ANY kind of plating so I don't THINK it's rhodium...

And CUTE? It's SO cute and replaces an old favorite I lost in a snowbank once, in fact, with the onyx it's a nicer piece than what I lost! The design is lovely... It's just that the color is just enough off to bug me a little.

Otherwise it's a sturdy, well made darling of a ring I'm hoping there was some protective coating effecting the color of the metal and that it'll wear off with time. Comfy too...

review_body:
I am very surprised at the look and the quality of this ring. The stones seem to be set really well and the cuts on the stones reflect the light to where it sparkles beautifully. I am quite impressed with the look, weight and thickness of the band and the gold plating adds to the appearance of the ring, which makes it look like it is solid gold. This ring not only looks expensive, but it feels expensive too. I accidentally dropped the ring and it landed directly on the face of the main stone. I was so upset thinking that the stone might have cracked or that the prongs on the setting would be damaged somehow, but the ring was still perfect, no loose stones and no damage. It looked just as it did when I first pulled it out of the jewelry bag. I really can't say enough about this ring....it is absolutely stunning!
I was able to purchase this ring at a discounted price in exchange for for my honest opinion and review.

product_title: Sterling Silver Women's Simulated Blue Sapphire Ring Classic 925 Band 12mm Size 11
review_headline: Nice look, Poor quality with even worse customer service
review_body: Purchased in February 2015  Admittedly this ring is very nice to look at- however mine was defective.  I have quite small hands and in my opinion the smaller the size (6 for me) the more the stones on either side get "lost" around your finger.  This ring probably would look/fit best on a size 8 or larger.  It is a bold and rich look despite the fact that ALL the stones are glorified colored plastic.  I knew this going in but again it is a very classy design in my opinion so I took a chance and got burned by the lack of quality and poor customer service at Sac Silver...  I had a major issue with rattling stones straight out of the package- So I never wore mine...  I contacted Sac Silver the day it arrived to tell them I could hear the 3 blue stones rattle when I shook it by my ear.  They replied telling me that if I wanted a refund on the defective ring I WOULD HAVE TO PAY to send it back.  I immediately contacted amazon resolution who saw through the games Sac was playing and promptly issued a full refund.

review_body:
I am in love. I ordered this for my sweet little princess for her birthday and I cannot wait to give it to her! I mean, you only turn 3 once, right?!

I was pleased to receive this I'm a cute little case; truly the perfect presentation for a gift. Upon opening, it was apparent that this is a quality item. The chain was strong and all of the connecting pieces look to be made well. This is NOT a basic, cheap necklace you might find at a dollar store. This is quality and sturdy, perfect for all ages.

We have not worn, obviously, but I will update my review once we have a chance to wear it about. I have no doubts and full confidence that there will be no disappointments. I did try it on and wear it around for the day, myself, with no issues (I wanted to see if it irritated the skin and such). This necklace is exactly as described and the best part is being able to customize for whomever you wish!

Glad to have the chance to purchase and review.

product_title: Sterling Silver Black and White Diamond Double Heart Pendant Necklace (1/3 cttw), 18"
review_body: I really like this necklace/pendant a lot! The stones are tiny, expect this. There is some color/saturation variance of the black diamonds. A couple shine more grey when the light catches them. This is only noticeable upon close examination and I really doubt anyone would notice it when it was being worn. To me, the size is just right, being neither too large nor too dainty. The chain is a perfect weight and size as well, and it is a smooth rolo chain which does not feel scratchy or catch my hair. It has a small elongated lobster clasp and the opposite loop end has a small bar which makes this dainty clasp a bit more handy to manipulate. It is very pretty and in my opinion looks classy (not overly trendy), timeless and ageless (not at all juvenile). I think the price is quite reasonable for a piece of diamond and sterling silver. The back of the  heart has the tiny light holes for most of the stone work, which indicates better workmanship. The bale on the heart threads the chain through two heart sections to keep the heart facing forward and presenting at an attractive slightly tilted angle. Two thumbs up!!

product_title: Cerceau 35mm Silver Plated Hoop Clip On Earrings
review_headline: I bought these on ebay from same seller, and ...
review_body:
I bought these on ebay from same seller, and thought they were a little fragile but seemed okay. Then after a few wearings there was no tension in one of the earrings and it wouldn't stay on. Just too cheap. There is another seller on ebay that is selling the exact same earrings for ~$5, so gives you an idea of quality and I wouldn't have bought them if I had seen that first.

I wrote the seller and he said that this has never happened unless the earrings were bent by the buyer. Well, they are as round as the day I got them (see pic). Not worth the time and money to exchange them, especially if you can get another new pair for $5 which is less than the money you would lose sending them back to AJ.

product_title: Halloween Jewelry Floating Charm Lockets Halloween Costume Jewelry Creepy Halloween Witch Charm Necklace
review_headline: This is a super cute necklace and who doesn't love a locket!??
review_body: [[VIDEOID:7a66276e2ae905e2f82c199c85de4e3e]]Is this perfect for Halloween? Yes it is. It is so amazingly adorable and different that there is no way anyone could not love this.    It's a floating charm necklace, but the locket is my favorite part. Ok, I take that back. It's one of my favorite parts. Because I also love and adore the floating charms. I got the purple witch hat with the black cat and the pumpkin. And there is 5 stones that are floating around in it also. So cute!    The locket is super simple to open, there's a lot on the side and it has a magnetic field so that you don't have to worry about it flying open. I like that you can change out the charms that can go inside, and not just wear for Halloween but year-round. If you choose. The stainless steel plate is engraved on one side and plain on the other. So it CAN be used year round!!!  Plus, there's still a good two months before Halloween so I have 2 months to wear this and then plan on what will go in it next! :) YAY FOR MEEEEEE!!!    I like the necklace, and it's a rolo ball chain, and I have absolutely no doubt that this will hold up and stand the test of time. The stainless steel locket I also have absolutely no doubt about it staying in its perfect form. Overall, I absolutely love this and I would recommend it to anyone. Having a floating charm locket is so much fun, and it makes a great gift!    I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do a review.

In a week, I received the correct size, but noticed scratches and flaws that had me very disappointed. Instead of staying dissatisfied and writing a bad review, I sent an email. I expressed how pleased I was with the first ring, but I ordered the wrong size and now this ring has so many scratches and flaws. I also mentioned I didn't mean to be a pain, but I'm just so disappointed. I received an email of apology, and that I will receive a pre paid postage to send it back so it can be fixed. I was so thankful and happy! I sent it back, and received it a week later polished, scratches and flaws removed! Thank you so much!

product_title: Diaura Sterling Silver Square Shape Diamond Stud Earrings
review_headline: Very pretty and excellent value for price. Wife loves them! Poor packaging.
review_body:
My wife loves these earrings. I've always wanted to get her diamond earring studs, but have never been able to afford a decent enough sized pair. Enter these square studs, and now I have a very happy wife.

These have a great contrast between the darker edges and the diamond centers. I'm not sure exactly how many carats there are, but the way they are cut they seem bigger and brighter than what you pay for. $50 would typically get you minuscule diamond studs, but here you get much bigger studs for the price.

They're not the most sparkly studs in the world, but for the price they are quite nice. I don't know what the darker stones are around the edge - it's not listed anywhere. But it's a nice contrast.

It comes in a very plain black box. There is no nice earring box - it's just a plain box with studs in it. The presentation was quite lacking, which made it feel like a "cheap" gift.

They have secure clasps on the back, though they do loosen over time so make sure you check them. They're sterling silver, which allows for a cheaper price. I wish they were platinum or white gold, but they definitely would've been much more expensive.

Overall they're a very good value, and I had low expectations. Definitely pleasantly surprised!
