review_headline: A cute bracelet to accessorize with an outfit.
review_body:
Got these two weeks before the expected arrival date so imagine my thrill as I tore this open today. It is exactly as pictured. Made of a cloth and leather feel bands. The silver charms look extremely cute on the bands and not too overwhelming to the bands. For the price I paid, I have added a few more of their other ones for personal pleasure. The clasp is the same as a necklace clasp. The extra silver chain that hangs after you hook it makes your wrist look more dainty ( not sure if that makes sense, I said that to my mom too and she just laughed....). The bands are attached to a silver vertical short bar. I tried pulling on it once it was attached to see how it would hold up to my roudh, careless handling and it didn't give by much. I'm certain if you truly exerted force it would snap of course but I only applied enough to see if it could handle snags on door knobs, hair pulls and various light sudden tugs.

product_title: Platinum or Gold Plated Sterling Silver Asscher-Cut Swarovski Zirconia Antique Ring Set (4.5 cttw)
review_body: Lovely set! We purchased this for several reasons - First, I've recently lost a lot of weight and my original wedding set it far too large and a simple resize won't work. So, we are considering having the diamonds re-set into something else. We are taking our time with it  and I don't like having a naked finger. Next, I travel for work and am sometimes in some sketchy situations. If something happens where I am mugged or attacked, I don't want to feel heartbroken about losing my rings. However, I didn't want something too plain either... for appearance reasons I needed something a little more "girly" - and I really wanted another yellow gold set with an antique look or feel. That's not a very easy thing to find these days when silver toned rings are in the majority. My skin color responds well to warmer tones, so I was thrilled to see this set available in yellow gold. It does feel a little large, but I have larger fingers so it works well. I received several compliments on it... many from people who assume it's a gift for being married for 15 years or after my weight loss. (The piece was broken at the dragonfly, not at the bracelet links)

The bracelet is made of 6 links that are about 1 inch long and one inch wide. They are held together with a thin elastic string that feels strong. The bracelet itself is 7 inches and the dragonfly is 3 1/4 inches wide and 2 inches tall. It's a nice large piece without a lot of weight. to drag your arm down.

It comes in a nice jewelry box that is suitable for gifting or keeping.

I received a discount on this product for testing and reviewing purposes and this is my honest and unbiased opinion.

product_title: Fashion Plaza Women's Cubic Zirconia Engagement Wedding Ring R474-6.5
review_headline: You May Want to Put Some Nail Polish on It
review_body:
I bought this as a fun replacement for my real engagement ring while I'm losing weight and don't want to have to resize multiple times. I made the mistake of not immediately painting the inside of the ring with clear nail polish, like normal. I do have really sensitive skin. It's a little bit flashy compared to my real engagement ring, but it's really fun. I can't speak to the sizing because I don't know my real size, so I took a guess, compared to my old size.
I probably won't wear it every day when I go out, since I ordered a nice eternity band for daily wear, but all girls like to have fun with flashy jewelry! And, I'm not an expert or anything, but it looks real to me. (As long as you don't turn it over and look at the scratches. It does scratch very easily, so I'm hoping my new coat of nail polish, which I will apply regularly will stop that).
Overall, you may want nail polish on it to prevent scratching and green skin, if you have sensitive skin.

product_title: 10mm Flat Men's Cobalt Free Tungsten Carbide Comfort-fit Wedding Band Ring (Size 8.5 to 14)
review_headline: Great ring, love the finish & color, but order it oversized...
review_body:
Love the ring, excellent finish (maybe a bit darker material than the picture shows, but I prefer the actual color). Beautiful ring, even happier with it in person. Sizes run a bit small IMO, I typically wear a size 7.5, so I ordered an 8. The 8 was MUCH too small, but with my wedding near, I couldn't wait for a return/replacement, so I simply applied for a refund and ordered a second in a size 9.

Unfortunately, when the replacement arrived, the vendor accidentally sent an 8.5. We contacted the vendor immediately, who was very easy to work with; they sent me a 9 via Priority Mail (I only opted for standard shipping when purchased), and included a self-addressed envelope with postage for the return of both the 8 and the 8.5. The 9 fits perfectly, ultimately I was happy with the product and the seller, they handled the replacement the way a vendor should.

product_title: European Beaded Charm Bracelet Pink Teddy Bear for Women and Teen Girls 7.5 Inch Prime Gift
review_body:
This bracelet is... beyond cute. Adorable is more like the perfect word. Not only is it really cute, this is made out of a surgical grade stainless steel, so it will resist corrosion. If you are allergic to nickel, you're fine wearing this. The stainless steel will keep your charms from being damaged, it will keep all of them safe. And, one of my favorite parts. You don't ever have to polish it. Sterling silver bracelets are all cute and great and wonderful. But once they start to tarnish and you have to spend an hour trying to make them look new again, it kind of takes away from the fact that you have a bracelet that you like. I think mine kind of starts to turn into hate because I really don't want to have to put that much work into a bracelet that used to be pretty. This one I don't have to worry about because it's stainless steel. :-)

The barrel is really easy to open and close. It has a snap clasp, so one handed is not an issue.

Okay, let's get to the charms. There is for silver color plated zinc alloy charms, there is the 9.25 silver little bear, and he dangles. Not a lot to where it's annoying, but the perfect size dangle. And then there are the four Murano lampwork clear glass charms. Those are really pretty, and they definitely add a ton of character, and makes the silver and the stainless steel pop!!!

I really like that the charms can be interchangeable, so if you don't like the cute little leaf charms that are on here, you can take them off and put something else back on. It works with any other of the European style add a bead bracelets or necklaces. You have a million and one options, and that in itself is really cool. You can change it to match your outfit! Or your shoes.

I really like this bracelet, I think this is a good gift either to yourself or to somebody that you care about. I think I'm going to have to stick with keeping it because it's really cute. But overall, it is beautiful, very well made, and durable.

I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do the review on my own.counted rate. I chose to do the review on my own.

review_body:
Just got it. The necklace length of 16" is true. The pearl beads look a little potato shape than "Round". The overall uniformity is good. The luster is actually quite better than "Medium- Luster" which they said in Product Spec. The surface blemishes are very light, also better than "moderately-blemished" which they said in Product Spec. I don't see any screw markings at all. The clasp is easy to work out. The package is very simple, no "several surprising extras" which was said in other reviews, but very enough for my own use.
With the price, it's very good quality. With the length and size, it's a good daily wear necklace. Definitely recommend !!!

product_title: BAMOER DIY European Style Love Heart Blue Crystal Murano Glass Bead Charms Fit Bracelets For Woman Girls 20CM 7.8"
review_headline: It's super cute, but the clasp is a little challenging.
review_body:
I love charm bracelets, but often find they are either too plain or too outlandish. This is a great bracelet with a bit of color, but not anything that's too far out there for my taste. I was impressed that the beads are exactly as pictured. I find sometimes pictures are deceiving, but this isn't one of those times. I particularly love the charm with the pink rhinestones and the turtle one best. The chain is sturdy and comfortable to wear. Each bead seems to be made very well, especially given the price of the bracelet.

I am marking this down one star for the clasp. My nails are thin right now since I don't have my gel polish on. I can't get this open by myself. It's also extremely difficult to put the bracelet on myself, I did finally manage to do it with some perseverance. There's a bead with "love" written on it that opens and a little ball that fits in there and closes to hold it shut. My husband can easily open it, but I can't. This is particularly frustrating since this ins't a bracelet that I will wear 24/7, it's something I will wear a few times a week. I would like to be able to put it on and take it off myself.

Overall, I can easily give it 4 stars and do really like it. If the clasp were more manageable I would definitely give it 5 stars. It's a wonderful price for such a cute bracelet. I was sent it to test and review, that in way influences my review. My rating and review are based on my experience with the bracelet.

product_title: DaisyJewel Star Spangled Dangle Earrings
review_headline: While these earrings are cute and nice to wear for a casual day out
review_body:
While these earrings are cute and nice to wear for a casual day out, they're nothing terribly fancy. The wires that the stars hook to are stiff and catch easily in awkward angles.

The stars themselves look like they were just hastily punched out of a sheet if metal with a hole punch. The edges are a bit rough and they look pretty flimsy.

While I don't mind them looking cheap too much, I don't feel they were worth the $20 or so that I spent. They do match pretty well with a necklace I have, so I'll hang on to them, but they won't be the first earrings I go for when I want to dress up a little more.

product_title: Sterling Silver Elongated Freshwater Cultured Pearl Framed Swarovski Zirconia Dangle Earrings
review_body:
These are nice, well made earrings that are very lightweight for their size. They do make my ear lobes droop a tiny bit, though. The pearl on each earring is lovely with a very nice shape and color. The metal used to make the earrings lends a little bit of a cheap look to them, in my opinion. I would agree with another reviewer who said it resembles chrome. Finally, I have bought and received quite a bit of jewelry from amazon in the past and it is typically packaged very nicely in lovely jewelry boxes suitable for gifting. Not so with these $100 earrings. I was disappointed there. So if you plan on gifting these, you may want to do something to spruce up the packaging.

UPDATE: I was bummed that I just now noticed that these do have a California Proposition 65 warning. Darn. The warning is listed on the page for this item online, but I didn't notice any warning material on the packaging of the actual item.

product_title: Celtic Cross Knot Aromatherapy Essential Oil Diffuser Necklace Locket Pendant Necklace
review_headline: I love using essential oils in my diffuser
review_body:
I love using essential oils in my diffuser, I've never heard of a locket for the oils until I got this locket. As you can see in the picture, that locket is beautiful. The leather cord holds it locket in place. There's a small disk that I put just a few drops of my oil on, than I closed the locket, there's a magnet that locks it and keeps it from opening.
The necklace comes to my collarbone which is great because I can breathe the essential oils all day long.
The locket has a little bit of weight to it, not much, which is great, the design on the locket is amazing. I've been wearing this locket for several days and it hasn't opened at all.
The only thing I wish it came with is extra felt pads so I can change the scents, however I'm going to be going to the craft store and pick up some felt and make it work. Overall it's a great locket, I'm very pleased with this product.

I received this product complimentary (or at a discount) in exchange for my honest opinion and unbiased review. These are just my own opinions and based on my personal experience.

product_title: Humble Chic Women's Y-Chain Bar Necklace - Adjustable Long Thin Delicate Chevron Choker Lariat
review_headline: This chain necklace looks very delicate and nicely made. It is available in two colors/tones
review_body:
This chain necklace looks very delicate and nicely made. It is available in two colors/tones. The chain is very lightweight and does not cause any irritation to the skin. I also had no issues with it snagging on my hair. I would definitely recommend avoiding any alcohol or perfume contact with the jewelry because it can lose the color. Water should also be avoided to prolong the life of an item.
The design of the chain is quite simple. Two chains joined together with solid bar at the ends. It looks nice when paired with the right color of clothes and style. You can even wear this to work, school or a casual evening out.
Overall it is nicely made with a simple yet durable and strong chain.
Sample provided without any obligations.

product_title: KONOV Mens Stainless Steel Bracelet, Classic Link Wrist, Black
review_headline: Simple and tasteful. Nice little bracelet.
review_body:
I like the bracelet. It's sturdy, looks good, and feels like good quality steel. It's simple and tasteful.

The shipping was a bit slow, but they were up front about that. Also, there was one small scratch near the buckle when it arrived, but luckily it is small, and that goes on the underside of my wrist, so it's not really an issue. Also, the clasp feels pretty sturdy, and I'm hopeful it will hold up over time. It's actually a bit hard to pop off sometimes, but you get the hang of it.

As far as the size, I think it should be adequate for most wrists. For me it was too big, but taking off a few sections was pretty easy. You just need an eyeglass screwdriver or something similar.

Ultimately, for the price, a nice little bracelet, and having perused some of the other Konov items, I would definitely buy from this seller in the future.

***A side note, I actually found the underside of the bracelet nicer than the actual outside, so I flipped the buckle and hinge portions and wear it inside out. The outside is a bit glossy for my tastes, while the inside has a really nice matte, sleek and simple look. So you actually have a bit of a choice which way to wear it.

product_title: Humble Chic Women's Lariat Bar Necklace Gold-Tone Circle Pendant Looped Long Chain, Gold-Tone Square
review_headline: I would highly recommend not letting the necklace come in contact with alcohol ...
review_body:
This circle and bar necklace is made delicately and with care. Even though the chain is very lightweight and simply made, the chain is atrong and durable. On one end of the chain there is a circle and a bar is attached to the other end. The bar passes through the circle. Therefore, you can actually adjust the depth of the necklace. There are no hooks to worry about and the necklace is safe to be worn. I would highly recommend not letting the necklace come in contact with alcohol or perfumes to avoid damage to the metal. The necklace is available in two tones/colors. This can be worn as a light piece to work or casually, or you can wear it with a leather jacket for a chic look. Either way it looks great, especially with free size sweaters.
Overall, this is made of good quality metal and looks nice.
Sample provided without any obligations.

review_body: I decided  to abandon  my fierce  loyalty  to Swarovski and instead  try a piece  of jewelry  with Swarovski  elements. First the positives  this ring came with a jewelry  pouch  to hold  the ring, paperwork  stating  care instructions,and  certificate  of authenticity. The ring is described  fairly  accurately. But here's  the reality...after careful  inspection  when you  place  the ring  on its side you can see that the crystals  are not set well possibly  glued.  They are not even and some  are set so poorly  that you can run your  finger along the edge  and feel the difference. Also these crystals  are not clear. They have a milky hazed  look.  The band itself is fine and has sheen. The stones are not. I bought  this  ring  as a compliment to my Swarovski  branded ring and I am unable  to wear them together  as their  is a major quality difference. I received  this  product  for  a  discount  in  exchange  for  an  honest  review and this is it.

product_title: European Charm Beaded Bracelet Vintage ?Made with Love? for Women, Teen Girls 7.5 Inch, Prime Quality ?
review_headline: This is beautiful and very well made!
review_body:
This is a really cute bracelet, it is 7 inches. That is a great size for a lot of teenagers and a lot of women. So it's a very versatile bracelet.

The colors are very vibrant! The platinum patina is the natural color of the particular steel that's used to make this, it's never going to wear off. It's a really high grade Metal, so it's not going to tarnish or turn colors.

That also means that it's really durable, and can withstand being born daily. I really like that the core isn't a threaded with anything, so you can take off the beads and design your own if you want. Which is so nice because having the option to change your bracelet around is fun!!!

This is definitely a eye-catching bracelet, I think it's the vibrant red with the gold, I don't know what it is that makes it stand out as much as it does except for the fact that it's just beautiful.

I like the way that the heart dangles, but it's not a gaudy or tacky dangle. It's a really cute, the size and everything about this is just outstanding. It's quality made, from the rhinestone glass charms to the bracelet underneath the charms, there's nothing that I dislike about this.

I received this product at a discounted rate. I chose to do the review.

review_headline: This is the perfect piece of jewelry to dress up a simple formal ...
review_body: Simply stunning! Being from South Louisiana, we attend a lot of formal Mardi Gras balls, Twelfth Night parties, Festival balls, etc.  This is the perfect piece of jewelry to dress up a simple formal or semi-formal gown. The necklace incorporates lots of colors and could really be paired with a multitude of things. I like big, chunky, glamorous jewelry, and this is definitely a stunner! I have a lot of my great grandmother's antique jewelry and this reminds me of something from the 1940's. The colors of the necklace remind me of the beaches of Cancun and the beautiful shades of blue waters and the yellow sunshine. It comes packaged in a red velvet drawstring bag. Mine came in with a stone missing, I assume from shipping, but I am working on getting it exchanged as I type. This is definitely not a cheap, lightweight piece! It is so much more than I expected and I was pleasantly surprised! I do not think you will be disappointed at all with this piece, especially for the price! I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

review_body:
I had to replace my engagement ring and wedding ring due to a (don't laugh) small lake mishap at my husband's family's cabin.

I chose this as my engagement ring, and the rose gold inlay version as the wedding band. My husband already had the titanum version of this ring because he has metal allergies, I love that design, so I chose these because I like heavier rings.

I think tungsten is my new favorite metal! This design is so ornate and beautiful, and I don't think my klutzy self is going to be ABLE to leave a mark on it. Honestly, I'm going to be telling anyone I know who's getting engaged or married to consider these rings.

product_title: Ring Resizer, Ring Magic Ring Safety Bands, TRIAL Pack 3 Assorted Sizes (1 Sm, 1 Med, 1 Lrg)
review_headline: I'll pay for innovation - I don't care if it's not more than what looks like a small hair tie)
review_body:
Unlike the other reviews, I paid actual money out of my actual pocket - and I wish I hadn't bothered. While the product is dead simple (hey, I'll pay for innovation - I don't care if it's not more than what looks like a small hair tie), it just doesn't work. I have two rings I wear on one finger that are too big by a size or so. I was super excited to try these - looked comfortable, and easy to use. And while they ARE comfortable and easy to use... they don't keep my rings in place. While they don't let them fall OFF - they are literally tethered to my hand - they don't keep them from slipping or sliding, and you can see the 'safety band' really really easily.

Save your $8. Try something else.

review_headline: appears very dainty and loved when I received
review_body: wish I had never paid this kind of money.  am soooo upset.  appears very dainty and loved when I received.  noticed what I would call an indentation in one of the curves when I put on the first time.  took this off for house keeping and showers so as not to damage.  after a couple of weeks I noticed the indentation was growing and becoming worse and became like a line in the gold.  three weeks ago I was taking it off before my shower and just the simple act of taking off turned the indentation into a full break.  i'll admit, I cried.  older woman, live on fixed income.  spending this kind of money to have worn it for maybe thirty days and then have it be unwearable thereafter.... sucks big time.  do not have contact info for seller.  to be fair it was enclosed with package but I threw away because I loved the look of the bracelet so much.  sick about the loss of money and not having something really nice to wear.  would not recommend a purchase.  it's beautiful and dainty but maybe not worth the money spent.

product_title: Impressive Chocolate Fever Brown Mens Leather Cuff Studs Bracelet
review_headline: Fits My 9" Wrist With Room To Spare
review_body: I will start off by saying I have larger wrists and it is hard to find bracelets that fit. I am glad I found this bracelet because it fits my 9 inch wrist in the middle hole perfectly. But the buckle on the bracelet is a large buckle and is a little uncomfortable when worn most of the day. Now onto the reason I gave it 3 stars. It is hard to tell when looking at the picture provided unless you know it's there, but there are 2 long slits running down the middle of the bracelet for about 4 inches. There is one slit in between the rivets running down the center and the white thread on the edge and the other on the opposite side. These run lengthwise from the 3 rivets on the buckle side to the other 3 rivets on the side with the holes. I think it may be made that way to make it more flexible but I really don't know for sure. I am just glad it fit my large wrist because it is a awesome looking bracelet.

Best plugs ever! I have a new view on life from this purchase!
RECOMMEND!

product_title: 6.5 MM Round Brilliant Cut Forever Brilliant¬Æ Moissanite by Charles & Colvard 57 Facets - Very Good Cut (0.88ct Actual Weight, 1.00ct. Diamond Equivalent Weight)
review_headline: I'm so glad I went with the Forever Brilliant version of the ...
review_body: This is such a stunning stone! It is very sparkly, is almost perfectly colorless (except for a very slight yellow, but barely), and it is flawless. I bought this stone to replace a cubic zarconia stone in a gold ring I have. I went to a local jeweler's shop, and for $65, they took out my CZ stone and replaced it with this Moissanite. I'm so glad I went with the Forever Brilliant version of the Moissanite. I have a pair of earring studs that are 1 carat each of Moissanite, but it's not the Forever Brilliant type, so the yellow is a little more evident. They both sparkle like crazy, though. This is perfect for people like me who like the sparkle of a diamond, and the hardiness of a diamond, but don't want the risk of buying a conflict diamond, or who don't want to shell out the money for an overpriced stone.

product_title: Brushed Titanium Wedding Band Ring With Stainless Cable Inlay and Blue Cubic Zirconia CZ
review_headline: For anyone that is wanting to know... THIS IS NOT A COMFORT FIT RING!
review_body: I like the fact that it kind of goes with my wife's ring.Took FOREVER to get it. I ordered on the 15 and didn't get it til the 27. The picture makes the stones in the ring look bigger, the ring itself is in the phtoto bigger as well. Not a whole lot of weight to the ring so it feels a little cheap. Because it is not a comfort fit ring (that is what I am use too) it cuts into the finger. This is a lot more noticeable when you take it on or off or your play with it as I will from time to time. (By that I mean I use both fingers on either sides of the ring to twist it on my finger) Don't know if I am the only one that does this... so if I am ... you shouldn't notice it being that uncomfortable. So in a nut shell (heavier ring, bigger stones, bigger ring confort fit, this would have been a 10!!! lol ) Hopes this helps .. anyone have any questions feel free to holler at me.

product_title: 14K White Akoya Cultured Pearl Classic Solitaire Pendant, 6.0-6.5mm, 16-Inch Chain, Yellow Gold
review_headline: I liked this chain and the pendant combination in the pic ...
review_body:
I purchased this pearl pendant for my birthday. I liked this chain and the pendant combination in the pic from all the other pendant necklace combinations that I viewed on Amazon.
On opening the package, I must say I was a little disappointed with the chain. It is much thinner and delicate than it appeared in the product photo.
I contacted the company's customer service rep. She was helpful and offered an upgrade on the chain at a price, but that was out of my budget. She also assured I could wear this chain on a daily basis. This chain will need some 'unwarping' during the day if you want it to appear as it does in the product photo.
The pearl itself seems good quality based on the Quality assurance certificate that comes with it. So you are really paying for the pearl and not so much the chain.
I'll keep the pendant and hope that the chain does not break.
Update Sept 25, 2015: Owners replaced the chain. Thanks much!

review_body: Just wanted to add. Great product, but they are NOT made of anodized titanium. Titanium cannot be anodized to be black. These are probably titanium underneath with a top coating of G23 Titanium, which usually has Aluminum and Vanadium in it. These are still perfectly safe for your ears and are a fantastic product, I just wish they weren't mislabeled like this. I am a jeweler and we usually use G23 Titanium in our black titanium pieces. I would reccomend these to anyone wanting to stretch their ears safely and without problems. Again, great, well manufactured product.

product_title: Unistyle Alloy Arrow Leather Pendant Necklace Brown 29"
review_headline: I fell in love with this necklace the moment I saw it
review_body:
I fell in love with this necklace the moment I saw it. I was hoping it would be a smaller arrow, but it is not. Therefore, I decided to give this to my oldest boy for his birthday. He has hugged a dozen times since. He loves it as well.
It's well made, and comes on a leather cord, that is adjustable. That way you can have it long or you can wear it short like a choker type necklace. He wears it both ways, depending on his mood and his outfit.
All the pieces seem like they are attached very well, and won't fall off anytime soon.
This comes with a gift box, and he keeps it in the box when he is not wearing it. That way it won't get lost or torn up.

product_title: Free Engraving - Stainless Steel Ladies Medical Id Bracelet
review_headline: Beautiful little piece for peace of mind
review_body:
I did a lot of research before settling on this model. Why? It has a strap that you can adjust, I wear it on the middle notch. It is stainless steel, which should last quite a while. The company did free engraving so I didn't have to try to track someone down. It is a very nice piece to wear everyday and could wear it along with another bracelet, if wanted.
For reference my wrist measures 6.5" around.
The length if you lay the bracelet out flat is 8"
The engraveable space is 1 1/8" x 5/8 wide (again after you order you contact the company by the contact seller button that will take you to instructions on what to engrave, I have 10 spaces used it is nice and big. They engrave straight onto the piece but you can still see it well)

Update
Yesterday I couldn't get the bracelet off I even enlisted help to try to free it. I had to get a pair of pliers to hold the metal that the end tucks into and still couldn't budge it. Then I had to pull and unforfunately it was caught very snugly and pulled apart, needless to say it had to be discarded. Until then it functioned fine, but was showing signs of annoyance it did stretch, which I expected, but the little metal part started sticking until it failed.

Forevergiftusa was whom I purchased it from and they were very diligent in making sure I got what I wanted engraved. It arrived in a timely manner, well protected.

product_title: INOX Men's Stainless Steel Black IP With CZs in the Center Hammered Finish Bracelet
review_headline: A very nice looking bracelet that is very well finished
review_body: A very nice looking bracelet that is very well finished.  It is made from 316L stainless steel.  This makes the bracelet solid but also makes it a bit heavier if that is an issue for you (I think it's a plus because you'll know if it accidentally comes loose).  The black surface finish is smooth even with the hammered finish.  The sides have a copper-tone finish concealing all joints between links.  It doesn't jump out at you -- it's just enough to make you want to look closer.  The same is true for the CZ on top.  They blend in with the black background so they aren't a distraction.  The bracelet has an extra clasp link so you can make it adjustable to approximately 8 inches from 8.25 inches.  I ended up returning it because unfortunately my wrist was still too small for this very nice bracelet.  The seller was very prompt in responding when I asked about re-sizing.  Bottom line:  If you want a quality bracelet that stands out from the rest, I recommend this one.  Just be sure to measure your wrist to ensure it will fit you and make you happy.

review_headline: Beautiful ring...broke on second wearing....replacement is great!
review_body: It pains me to only give this one star...however, it also pains me to pay $30 for a ring, only to have it break a couple of days past the return window, even though I only wore it twice. One of the purple stones fell out, rendering it unwearable without looking stupid. It was very pretty for the two times I wore it, but not worth the per-wear cost. Extremely disappointed that I can't return or exchange this defective ring and will think twice about purchasing from the Amazon collection again.  8/30/15 update: Upon contacting Amazon about this, they sent me a replacement, which arrived the very next day. I will see how it holds up and then update my review.  11/27/15 update: I've worn it a few times, and it's still holding up well, and looks nice, too. :) 4/7/16: I've worn the second ring a lot, and it is still holding up well, and looks beautiful.

We pressed the button down to pop open the lid and show the time. We turned the black knob to the right time. And he was ready to go. My daughter who is 16 and knows nothing about Harry Potter begged him to let her wear it that night to a party. She thought it looked cool. He refused. He removed it from the necklace and walk around with it in his hand or pocket. He shows all his friends and they are very impressed. Our little one likes to wear it and for the price point, it is a fun piece of jewelry for her. I would be afraid to attach anything heavy or of value but I feel it was listed as being used for that anyway. For the price and quality, it is exactly as described.. a silk cord rope necklace.

product_title: Rhodium Plated Sterling Silver Birthstone Cross Pendant Necklace, 18"
review_headline: Delicate, pretty, but needs a better chain
review_body:
This is a really lovely, delicate necklace. The only thing I don't like about it is the chain.

This necklace is really pretty. It is very small and delicate, so it isn't for women who like chunky jewelry. The cross is small enough that it could even be used as a charm on a bracelet.

My only qualm is the chain. The chain is very delicate and, I think, will break pretty easily. It is also hard to clasp, so I need to get necklace magnets to make it easier.

The chain is also not going to be long enough for anyone plus size. It also knots up easily if you don't hang the necklace up right.

The one I received had purple stones that were rich in color. The stones are held tightly in place by design, so I don't think there is a change of losing any right away.

Overall, this is really pretty. I would recommend it for women who like delicate jewelry and even as a gift for young girls. It comes in the standard Amazon Collection black box with the velvet lining, so no wrapping required!

product_title: KONOV Mens Stainless Steel Ring, Gothic Skull Cross, Black
review_body: The ring is excellent and true to size though I do have two minor complaints. The skulls on either end of the cross are not like those in the picture. They have been filed down to be almost flush with the cross giving them an odd flat appearance. I imagine this will minimize the ring catching on my pockets though so it might be for the best. Secondly, the golden cross area has significant scratching on one of the arms. I plan to wear the ring everyday so I  planned for it to get slightly beat up, I just didn't expect to arrive with scratches on it. Overall, the ring is wonderful and the issues I've stated are almost insignificant, I just wanted to share them.  I will say that shipping did cause me some anxiety. I am spoiled by Amazon Prime so waiting two weeks was torture. The item shipped ChinaPost EMS and then via USPS. USPS was horrible at updating the tracking info but the item arrived within the stated time and towards the earliest end of the estimate.  UPDATE: After a week of constant wear I haven't noticed any discoloration to my finger or the ring. I thought maybe there would be when I noticed a lack of markings inside the ring denoting 316L steel. There is some sort of clear finish or maybe polishing compound that has been flaking off but no issues.

product_title: 10K White Gold Oval Tanzanite and Round White Topaz Ring, Size 7
review_headline: I reordered the ring and paid for 1 day shipping hoping for better luck. The second ring came in today with ...
review_body:
A few things about this:

I order this ring 3 days before my girlfriend's birthday. it arrived the day before with 2 day shipping. One of the clear stones was missing and the minor diameter of the ring was .62" at its smallest point while a size 7 ring is supposed to be .682" inner diameter. So the ring didn't fit and it was missing a stone.

I reordered the ring and paid for 1 day shipping hoping for better luck. The second ring came in today with a minimum inner diameter of .67 inches which should actually fit. The stones were all there and the ring looked nice.

It seems like there are manufacturing issues going on. If you get a good ring, you'll do fine. Order well in advance to be sure that you don't get a garbage product.

product_title: European Red Love Charm Bracelet Be My Valentine for Women Teen Girls 7.5 Inch Professional Quality
review_body:
This is a great Valentine's Day gift. I say it's Great Valentine's Day gift because there is a cute little hard on it that says be my valentine. That being said, if you choose to you take that off you can. This bracelet comes with 2 o rings to keep the charms on but it's also made to take them off. You can replace them with other beads, and the core isn't threaded so it's not difficult at all.

The clasp on this bracelet is really nice, it's easy to open with one hand, although, granted to Hans is better but if you don't have somebody around who can help you, you can definitely do it yourself.

This bracelet has four Murano lampwork clear glass charms, for silver color plated zinc alloy charms, it has a vintage 925 silver plated crown single bead. And then it has the European-style charm, it comes in a gift box that is really cute and makes for the best gifting, especially since I despise wrapping. I'm just not patient enough for that.

It's really pretty, and it's different. I think that this really would be a great gift. I wore it and it didn't catch on my arm hair, and it didn't pinch me. I was not necessarily worried about that, but I kind of kept waiting for it to happen. It used to happen when I was wearing one of those super ridiculously expensive name brand starts with the P and ends with anDora. I would get pinched a LOT. That was a good gift for someone else... That would not be the same reason that I would ever gift this one, I would gift this because it's really cute. Not because I hated it.

I received this product at a discounted rate. I choose to do this review on my own.

product_title: JewelrieShop 20G Nose Ring Hoop Stainless Steel Nose Piercing Body Jewelry Set
review_body:
I just got these yesterday and overall I am VERY pleased! I DO NOT have my nose pierced, but noticed that someone said these could be worn as a piercing OR as a "clip on" nose piercing. For $7 I decided to give it a try. I work at a bank but have ALWAYS wanted a piercing and this seemed like a good solution. I LOVE it!

TO THOSE WHO ARE WEARING IT AS A FAKE PIERCING: The nose rings look very real. The ONE thing I think people should know going in is that you will most likely have to do some bending/adjusting when fitting the ring to your nose. It took me about 5-10 minutes to carefully bend the rings to fit to my nose well. I have a smaller nose so that may be why. Overall they look real, wear well once fitted, and are worth doing a little extra work for the great price! Take your time bending them and you'll love them! :)

product_title: Aiyaya Round Silver Zircon Sparkling Crystal Rings for Women Sz6
review_headline: The band is made of 18k gold plated metal that shines just like white gold
review_body: This ring is not so over the top flashy that everyone knows it is a cz. The band is made of 18k gold plated metal that shines just like white gold. It has channel set diamonds on the band. It is topped with a round brilliant CZ that is about 1/4 of a karat. It is a truly believable ring that any woman would love to wear on her hand. The CZ's shine just like diamonds. The ring has a very low profile, so it shouldn't bother anyone that has to wear gloves for their job. It is a very dainty ring, and comes packaged in a red velvet bag. The ring comes with a one year warranty, so you will get lots of wear without worrying about messing it up. I like to wear cz's when I am out in New Orleans or other big places. I don't want to be hurt or killed over jewelry, so this way, I could just hand it over. I also like the fact that you don't have to worry about losing it if you have a few too many drinks. ;-) I received this product at a discount in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: Sterling Silver Elongated Freshwater Cultured Pearl Framed Swarovski Zirconia Dangle Earrings
review_body:
These earrings are quite lovely for a fancy evening. They aren't too heavy (sometimes dangly earrings start to feel like bowling balls after an hour or so!), and catch the light quite nicely. Though these are crystal and pearl, the pearls especially are of a nice quality. The crystal catches the light nicely, but a close inspection reveals them to not be diamond chips - so there is a level of fanciness that these are appropriate for, and a level in which they are not quite fancy enough... So, you may not wear them as frequently as other, more versatile earrings as these really can't be "dressed down" without looking ridiculous!

I think the price fits in with the mid-range of the fancy-levels of places that you can wear these. I wouldn't wear them during the day, but they are great for sprucing up a nice night out on the town!

product_title: 8MM Black Ceramic Wedding Ring Natural Acacia Koa Wood Inlay Comfort Fit
review_headline: Love the color, little too shiny, very light
review_body: Lost my first $20 wedding band (Tungsten) and wanted the wood grain look this time around. Overall, I've been very satisfied with the ring and the sizing was spot on. Some things to point out, though. First off, I wanted beveled sides and this delivered. Another reason I chose this over other black tungsten rings, was because apparently black is ceramic's natural color, whereas black tungsten is black metal injected into it to make it black. It has a higher probability of showing wear and scratches because it's no it's natural color and  I'd have to say I like the natural gunmetal black color much better than just plain black.  Something that might throw some off, though, is the shininess of the ring. I half expected the wood part to be more of a semi gloss finish, but this ring shines all the way around. In the sunlight, the wood grain looks the best and really stands out and has a neat color to it; however, in lower light or indoor light, it's much harder to really see the wood grain style through the shininess of the ring. I don't mind it, but you might.  One last thing, this is my first experience with ceramic rings as my last was tungsten. I really got used to the weightiness of the tungsten and made me feel a little better knowing it was a heavier piece of metal. This ring is complete opposite in weight compared to my tungsten. Feels like a feather. It's something I grew accustomed to very quickly, but did not like at first. Ceramic is still almost as tough as tungsten, but if you like a weighted feeling ring, I don't suggest ceramic.  All in all, you're not spending that much on the ring so, if you've got a problem with it, there's a million other rings out there. I couldn't have asked for much more. I love it cause it suits my personality and my wife loves it, too. That's what really counts, anyway, right?!

product_title: EleQueen Women's Crystal Simulated Pearl Elegant Wedding Pendant Necklace Earrings Jewelry Set Ivory Color
review_headline: THIS IS A BEAUTIFUL BRIDAL SET OF PEARL AND CRYSTAL JEWELRY
review_body:
This set of pearl and crystal necklace and earrings by EleQueen is very classy and timeless. The costume setting of the faux pearl and the Austrian crystal is quite believable. Noone would know by looking at the set that is was not a cultured pearl and diamonds. The pearl is what I would call a creamy off white and the crystals are clear. The set I have is the silver color and it is not garish and has the look of white gold. The pendant is not fixed, meaning it is not held in one place on the chain. This is good because it will not hang lopsided on you. The chain is adjustable (by attaching the clasps at different lengths), fitting 16-18 inches. The earrings match the necklace pendant exactly and are the post type earrings. EleQueen included the wide backs for stability, and also included the little clear plastic backs. I like the plastic backs best with these earrings, they are light enough to wear you do not need to have the wider one to make them hang right. This is a better set of costume jewelry. I have been collecting costume jewelry for over twenty five years and am able to recognize a nice quality piece. I feel confident telling you this would be a nice set for a gift or to wear for your wedding. It is beautiful and well made. The classy set of earrings and necklace comes in a swirl Tiffany blue gift box and a pretty pink velvet pouch is tucked inside also. So if this is going to be a gift, it will be ready upon arrival.
I purchased this jewelry set at no cost in return for an honest and unbiased review. I based my review on my own opinion and experience with the set of jewelry.

review_headline: Needed Cleaning Right Out of the Box. Otherwise Nice Looking!
review_body: Cute! The 18" necklace chain is very tiny but is actually more sturdy than it appears. It is barely visible when worn. The Peace Pendant is about the same size as a quarter and is a lovely design. The one received for review had tarnish at the top arc of the pendant between the chain attachment points. It came off with some polishing. There was also a white powdery looking residue between all weld joints. It did not come off. This one doesn't seem ready for prime time as is doesn't look the same as the stock photo which shows a flawless, polished and shiny version. I hope this gets "cleaned up" before too many of them ship out. Giving it 4 stars for now. It is still nice looking, just not flawless like the photo.

product_title: EVER FAITH Gold-Tone Rhinestone Crystal Party Art Deco Necklace Earrings Set Multicolor
review_body:
I'm always astonished at the quality of Ever Faith jewelry, especially when considering the price. This set is no exception, except that it's even more outrageously gorgeous than usual! The colors are outstanding, saturated, succulent jewel tones. These are the colors every gemstone wishes it was! The ruby red in particular jumps out at you, but you have sapphire blue, emerald green, peridot green, Morganite pink, canary diamond, and golden topaz colors, too. There are emerald cut stones, pear cut, baguette cut, cushion cut, square cut, and round brilliant cuts that all catch the light. The light is refracted and reflected off these colors and cuts, dazzling the eye and framing your face in opulent sparkle and juicy color. You will be noticed in this necklace, but then that's kind of the idea, isn't it? Lol! It's a great piece to wear in the summer, because it will go with all the primary colors women wear so often at that time of year. It'll work well on our patriotic summer holidays...wear this with a bright blue sundress or a white pantsuit...perfection! Because of the jewel tones, it'll work great at Christmas, too. Wear this to your company Christmas party, and you'll be sure to turn heads and get compliments!

It's a solid, well-built piece of jewelry, and it will last for years if not generations. You will be aware of it around your neck, but it's not heavy, just solid. The earrings are also beautiful, and have enough presence to be worn alone. A white blouse, a red wrist watch and these earrings will make an impact, but in a more subtle kind of way. You should be able to wear this set in most offices, and it would be a great set for casual events. Out to lunch, book club, baby shower, that sort of thing. I'd wear this more formally also, like to an evening wedding, but that may not be a look that appeals to you. You know who you are if you love big, bold colorful jewelry like I do.

This is about a 20" necklace when worn at its longest. I like a 19", so I won't need an extender this time. It's very comfortable, and well-articulated so it moves with you, allowing for even more light play around your face. The large stones are surrounded by small pave' rounds of every color you can think of. That creates even more sparkle and dance, and we can never have too much of that! The stones are very dimensional, too, which adds even more to the visual interest.

Ever Faith has this design available in monochromatic colorways, but I'm delighted I picked the multi. It gives me more options of how to wear it, but it also brings out the dimensions and flow of the design to better effect, imo. I wish I could give this more stars....it's the most beautifully executed design and the most sturdy necklace I've purchased in quite some time. This is a winner, people, so grab it while you can. All of this gorgeousness won't last forever!orn at its longest. I like a 19", so I won't need an extender this time. It's very comfortable, and well-articulated so it moves with you, allowing for even more light play around your face. The large stones are surrounded by small pave¬¥ rounds of every color you can think of. That creates even more sparkle and dance, and we can never have too much of that! The stones are very dimensional, too, which adds even more to the visual interest.

Ever Faith has this design available in monochromatic colorways, but I'm delighted I picked the multi. It gives me more options of how to wear it, but it also brings out the dimensions and flow of the design to better effect, imo. I wish I could give this more stars....it's the most beautifully executed design and the most sturdy necklace I've purchased in quite some time. This is a winner, people, so grab it while you can. All of this gorgeousness won't last forever!

product_title: Rose Gold and Rhodium Plated Sterling Silver Two Tone Diamond Butterfly Pendant Necklace (1/10cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity), 18"
review_headline: Gorgeous, quality pendant but lacking symmetry
review_body:
I love rose gold jewelry and butterflies have become quite symbolic in my life so I was really excited about this necklace. What I love about this piece:

-The rose gold and silver coloring is absolutely gorgeous. I love pieces that utilize cuts and facets of silver to create sparkle where stones would otherwise be required to achieve the same effect.

-The intricate design of the butterfly itself is beautifully done: not too elaborate, not too simplistic.

-The weight of this piece is impressive. The pendant feels solid and is smooth on the back.

-The 18" chain is just right in length and although it a lightweight chain, it seems to be considerably sturdier than many other stock chains I've received with pendants.

-The tiny stones scattered here and there along the outer edge of the butterfly's wings (10 stones in total) were unnecessary in my opinion but add a neat dynamic to the overall appearance of the pendant. The color/clarity of these stones isn't the greatest but as tiny accent stones they're just fine.

Unfortunately there is one issue that prevents me from giving this pendant a five star rating:

The first thing I noticed when I opened the box is that the two wings are not the same size. The wing that attaches to the chain is noticeably shorter and appears to also be narrower than the other (I will be uploading a photo of this). Also, the two wings do not connect to each other at the same point (causing one wing to sit a bit higher than the other). It is hard to note these characteristics when looking at the stock photo but they are quite evident in person. Thinking maybe I was being too nitpicky I handed the necklace to my husband and asked him if he noticed anything unusual about it. He glanced at it and said "the wings are two different sizes."

Overall, as mentioned the necklace and pendant are quality made and gorgeous. I'm not sure whether the asymmetry wasintentional or not but as far as my personal taste goes I would've preferred that the piece be symmetrical.

So far, this necklace has held up well. He has worn it for a day, however, he attended a church event that was a very intense, two hour obstacle course. He worried that it might break but he decided to leave it on and when him up, all was great. This necklace has a uniform look...good for both girls and boys alike. The chain is a higher quality leather and seems to be made well. Sometimes, the jewelry has a problem with pulling his hair, but with this chain, it has yet to happen. The clasp is a larger clasp so it would hold up too. How long is the question and we should find out. For now, all is happy here.

product_title: LEADCIN Stainless Steel Mens Bracelet Bike Chain Wide Motorcycle Heavy Bangle Man Jewelry
review_headline: Striking Look ... Though It Is A Bit Heavy
review_body:
As I mentioned in a recent review, I‚Äôve only really begun exploring men‚Äôs jewelry in the past few years. Oh, I‚Äôve always been interested in designer watches, pins, and the like; but there was just something about bracelets (in particular) that often kept me from trying them out. However, after I indulged myself in a few, I discovered that there‚Äôs a strong interest in dressing a bit differently from the next bloke, and consequently my curiosity was piqued.

LEADCIN has some very nice looking alternatives available online via their Amazon store, and they offered me the opportunity to try out this Stainless Steel (Blue) Bicycle Chain model. I‚Äôm wearing it right now as I pen this review.

As with most bracelets, it‚Äôs a bit difficult to get it clasp quickly: that‚Äôs no fault of LEADCIN or necessarily of the jewelry. This is just a task men have always done when putting them on a lady‚Äôs wrist; putting in on your own is a much different animal. However, once you get the angle just right, it goes on easily, and the clasp is certainly nice and tight.

As for the look of this one? It‚Äôs a deep, rich shade of blue (almost the classic 80‚Äôs/90‚Äôs Superman blue, and I‚Äôm wondering if that might not be of interest to some males?). It‚Äôs assembled from bike/motorcycle chain material, and thus it is relatively heavy on my wrist. That isn‚Äôt a distraction; rather it‚Äôs just another solid reason why you‚Äôll want to have this one properly sized to fit your wrist by a jeweler. Otherwise, it‚Äôs going to bob around more than you‚Äôd probably want. There are also plenty of silver/chrome highlights to it for those of you who prefer to ‚Äòmix it up‚Äô (color-wise).

I‚Äôm probably not liking it as much as the last item I tested from LEADCIN, but that isn‚Äôt to say it‚Äôs inferior. It‚Äôs just a bit heavy. The colors are excellent, and I‚Äôd encourage you to pick one up if these things are in your wheelhouse. Definitely a striking look.

Recommended. Though this one is a bit heavier than what I‚Äôve grown accustomed to, it definitely looks nice and shiny on my wrist. In fact, it might be a bit too shiny for my particular tastes, but it looks like an exceptional designer-style piece for the discriminating male.

In the interests of fairness, I‚Äôm pleased to disclose that the fine folks at LEADCIN provided me with sample testing product of their Stainless Steel Men's Bicycle Bike Chain Bracelet by request for the expressed purposes of completing this review; and their contribution to me in no way, shape, or form influenced my opinion of it.itely a striking look.

review_body:
Charmed bracelets seem to be all the rage at the moment, and I have been searching high a low for a beautiful quality charm bracelet that won't break the bank. The bracelet arrived extremely quickly way above the scheduled arrival date which I really appreciate. Each and every bead on this bracelet is beautifully made and adds just the right amount of "bling" to the overall look of the bracelet. If you're looking for a beautiful but inexpensive charm bracelet for yourself or as a gift you have to give this one a try!

review_headline: Great reviews to I decided on this necklace
review_body: Great reviews to I decided on this necklace. It is a beautiful necklace, but it arrived with 2 large kinks in it because of the way they packaged it. The box was very large but the necklace was double around in a circle and was very tightly wound around 4 pegs in the box. As a result there were 2 kinks in the necklace where it was wrapped around the pegs. If they had just sent it loose in a nice box, it probably would have been fine. But glad it happened now since some snake necklaces can be prone to kinking. Which is why I went for the more expensive diamond cut one. But apparently not as good quality as I had thought. Returning it and will continue to look.

product_title: MAZU Pearl Zircon-Accented Ring AA+ Quality Top022 Color Rose Gold
review_headline: Absolutely beautiful ring that accents any outfit
review_body:
I wasn't sure about how I would feel about this ring when I purchased it. When ordering the ring, I was a bit disappointed that there weren't more sizes to choose from. As someone who typically wears a size 9, I was almost hesitant to even order the ring. I took a chance when buying said ring, and I'm glad that I did. The only truly disappointing thing about this ring is that it didn't come in a box to match it. This ring is absolutely beautiful, and honestly photos don't really do it justice. For me, it's a little bulkier than what I typically would wear in a ring, but overall, it works well. The rose color goes with pretty much anything I wear, and it works well with any skin tone. As someone who has more olive skin, I loved that about this ring. I would definitely purchase it again at full price, if there were more extended sizes offered.

I received this item at a discounted cost for an honest review.

product_title: Trusuper 2MM Stainless Steel Black Rolo Cable Chain Necklace for Men Women, 16-36 inches
review_headline: Trusuper Stainless Steel Necklace Is Very Strong And Durable! Would Be Great For Any Male Or Female!
review_body:
This Trusuper Stainless Steel Necklace is very well made and sturdy! The snake chain is really nice and strong which makes me feel like it won't break very easily and when it comes to jewelry the less breakable it is the better. The silver color on this necklace is really nice and shiny and will definitely stand out. I received the 20inch necklace and on my not so small neck it fits really comfortably without being too short or too long. I actually have a longer box chain necklace that I never take off and I can wear this necklace without worrying about it covering up my other necklace.

This does say it's a man's necklace but there is nothing about this necklace that seems to be ONLY for men. I love that this necklace is stainless steel as it won't rust and doesn't irritate my sensitive skin. It will look great on women as well and I have no shame in wearing this "man" necklace. This necklace does come in a nice little gift bag which makes it gift ready and is a great gift idea for a man, woman, or even a child. I would definitely recommend this Trusuper Stainless Steel Necklace!

**I received a discount on this product for testing and reviewing purposes and this is my honest and unbiased opinion**

product_title: Burnished Gold Tone Hoot Owl Open Black Rhinestone Eyes Dangle Earrings
review_body:
Wow, I get to be the first to submit a review for these earrings! These are SO cute yet classy and not too over-the-top owl-y (is that a word?? Lol) I love these! This is probably my third pair of owl earrings, but I didn't have any like these until now. Here's my rundown:

PROS:
-Weight - these are heavy enough to stay in your ears and not pop out the moment they get caught on your hair (a major problem with cheap earrings). Yes, these are not too heavy in a way that would be uncomfortable.
-Style - I feel like these are totally appropriate for all ages due to the subtle and high-quality contours. I feel fine wearing these to work without getting teased or anything. :)
-Quality - even upon close inspection, these seem to be really high quality without the minor defects you often see in earrings like this.

CONS:
-Color - I felt that these were a bit more of a yellow gold than I expected based on the photos and the description. They are a burnished rather than straight yellow gold, but they are more yellow than the photo shows. I included photos here of me wearing them, but even those don't really show it properly. It might just be my computer; I do not think it's the fault of the seller, so I won't dock it a point. They're still so cute that I will wear them anyway (and again, they're really not very yellow, I just am not a fan of yellow gold at all.)

I received a discount on these earrings (not free) in exchange for my honest opinion. However, I picked these out specifically because they are totally "me", and I can definitely attest to their quality! I was not compensated in any way, nor am I affiliated with the manufacturer. I really like these earrings!

product_title: 590700HV-23 Authentic Pandora Sterling Silver Lobster Clasp Bracelet 9.1
review_body: Been wanting a REAL one of these for a very long time and finally went for it. I border on small/medium sized wrist (6.5") but my hands are big so the 9" bracelet won't easily slide off on me, I'd have to slide it off with soap. It's hard to find bangle bracelets (not hinged) this big so I thought I'd give this Pandora system a try. I don't like my bracelets snug on my wrist and I figure eventually with all the beads I'll add, it will fit just right (the way I like it). I plan on getting a safety chain for mine. YouTube has plenty of tutorials explaining the bracelet system and charms. review_body:
I've never seen a clasp like this before, and I love it. You pop open the "Love" bead and insert the other end of the chain into it, then clasp the bead closed. It fastens securely with an audible snap, and I can do it myself without having to ask someone to help me open or close the bracelet.

The glass beads are beautiful and worth the price of the bracelet by themselves. The other beads don't look expensive, but they're fine for what they are-- inexpensive costume jewelry. I hadn't noticed in the picture that there are turtle beads on both sides... cute!

As for sizing, I'm a petite woman and the 20 cm is a little big on me. (Not big enough to fall off, but I probably would have been better off with the 18 cm.)

The only other drawback is that it comes in just a clear plastic bag. Would be nice to have a box for gifting, but they're obviously trying to keep the price down, so that's a tradeoff.

review_headline: I love the wood inlay of this ring!
review_body: I love this ring! The listing describes it as an engagement ring or a wedding band, but it can easily be a really classy right-handed ring as well.  This ring is very unique with the wood inlay between the silver polished band, and the two together are a great match.  The ring fit really comfortably on my husband's finger and is a nice change from the gold band I bought him 20 years ago.  There is a protective coating around the entire outside which is smooth to the touch but will be interesting to see how it holds up from scratches over time.  The inside of the band is curved or "comfort fit" so theres not a straight edge that can be uncomfortable when you put the ring on.  I love the way Titanium is lightweight! Overall for the price point of this ring it is one I would highly recommend! I received this ring at a discount in exchange for my honest review.

product_title: bOdfx Stainless Ear Gauges Stretching Kit + Piercing Balm - 36 Piece Stainless Tapers & Tunnels. 14g-00g
review_body: I've had my ears pierced for 2 years now and I've been wanting to stretch them. All the reviews on this drew me in and I have to say, it's actually a great deal. I always hear people saying how they get allergic reactions to certain piercings, I never thought much into it because I never had an allergic reaction. Be mindful that I've had white gold, surgical steel, and sterling silver through my ears before. It's been a month since I got these and I'm already on 12G, but for the past 2 weeks my ears cannot stop itching. They're getting extremely dry and the irritation is starting to spread to my upper ear. I massage Vitamin E Oil into my ears daily, as most sites recommended, and I can't determine if that's helping or hurting this dry skin problem. I did a little research into it and I found out most "Stainless Steel" products contain nickel which is likely to cause the allergic reactions. If you haven't had allergic reactions to any piercings, these are for you. If your ears are even slightly on the sensitive side, look for surgical steel stretching kits.

product_title: Sterling Silver 1mm Box Chain Necklace, 14" - 36"
review_headline: This is a beautiful, strong chain
review_body:
This is a beautiful, strong chain. I bought it to wear with a Celtic cross pendant and it looks great! The chain itself is about the perfect thickness - not so thick that it's hard to affix pendants to, but also not so thin that it feels cheap (or looks particularly feminine). And since it's real sterling silver, it doesn't leave your neck green like those cheap chains from Claire's!

Overall, a great investment at a great price. Oh, and Amazon's picture of the 22-inch version of the chain has a weird "bubble" on the chain opposite the clasp. Rest assured that's just some artifact in the picture; the actual chain has no such feature.

product_title: Sterling Silver Created Dark and White Sapphire Emerald-Cut Drop Pendant Necklace, 18"
review_headline: nice silver chain and accents around a synthetic blue sapphire
review_body:
This is a pretty necklace. I really like the silver chain and the accents around the blue "sapphire" stone. I'm just not too sure what to think of the stone. as the description reads, it's created sapphire - meaning it is synthetic - think cubic-zirconia. Also, not sure why the title says it is white, clearly it is blue, just like the photo.

It hangs a tad low for me, I'd actually prefer it just a bit shorter, but it's pretty close. It did come in a black box with a small velvety pouch to put it in. However the necklace was in a plastic baggy and had a little "made in China" tag on it. There are some good products that come out of China, but the reputation here in the states is that means "cheap" so if you're giving this for a gift, be sure to get that tag off! (it comes off easy, just a little string holding it on).

This dainty Rose Gold Cross Pendant Necklace and Earrings Set is great for kids, teens and adults. The set comes in a beautifully decorated gift box so it‚Äôs ready to gives to a loved one. The earrings are approximately 7/16‚Äù x 3/8‚Äù. Each earring features 6 clear crystals. The earrings have standard butterfly backs and the posts have a single groove to help the backs stay on. The necklace is simply gorgeous. The gold cross pendant features 11 crystals on the front of the cross and 6 crystals on each side. The pendant is able to slide freely on the dainty gold chain. The chain is 18‚Äù long with a 2‚Äù extender. It has an easy top open round clasp and a tiny decorative stamped tag.

I personally love wearing this set myself. It‚Äôs great for when you want something small to wear every day. The adjustable chain makes it great to wear short or longer. I wear the earrings as studs in my second ear holes. This would make a great gift option for lots of occasions. product_title: Pro Jewelry .925 Sterling Silver "Functioning Crystal Genie Lamp" Charm Bead 029
review_body:
I was looking for a charm that would represent my love of lamps, different cultures, and Aladdin on my pandora bracelet, but each lamp charm I found had the bracelet hole going right through the middle of the lamp in a way where you couldn't even tell it was a lamp unless you took the whole bracelet off your wrist (what's the point of having a charm when you have to remove it from your bracelet to properly view it?).

This charm is MUCH MORE than what I was looking for!

1) It's a dangle, so I don't have the bracelet hole going through the actual lamp
2) It is a proper size (not too giant or too tiny), so it fits with the rest of my charms
3) It has intricate details carved into it
4) The spout and lid of the lamp has turquoise/light blue gems placed into it, giving the charm some color. There are also some clear/diamond colored gems around the charm ring itself for extra bling!
5) Apparently other lamp charms that have a lid that opens and closes will open and close on it's own, and reviewers of these charms have complained (and displayed pictures) of the lid being broken off because there was no way to securely close the lid. The lid on THIS charm not only opens and closes, but it also has a clasp so the lid can snap shut and stay securely closed until you're ready to open it!

I definitely recommend this lamp charm!

product_title: Sterling Silver White Diamond with Pink Plating Pendant Necklace (1/3cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity), 18"
review_headline: A little musical note made of diamonds on sterling
review_body:
A family member looked at the picture of this necklace on the Amazon site and immediately said of the pendant, \\"It's a musical note!\\" I can see that - now - and actually taken that way it is much more elegant than something stamped to look exactly like a musical note.

I'm a little iffy about Amazon Collection jewelry. For my personal tastes, a lot of it has too many big stones: zirconium, created or semi-precious. I'm not a big fan of the rhodium that (to me) makes some of the collection's jewelry look a bit costume, even if rhodium is unto itself a costly and rare metal

That said, this necklace exceeded my expectations. I did read the product specs before selecting this necklace, and based on the light weight and I2-I3 clarity (\\"good cut\\"), I did expect a smaller piece with duller stones than what I received. In this case, the item I got lived up to the product photos.

That doesn't mean that I'd say the piece is perfect. If you zoom on the product picture, the round part of the pendant, on the outer circle of diamonds at the 9:00 position, there are \\"empty\\" prongs showing that I at first took for missing stones, but in fact are just there to give the piece visual continuity from a medium close distance - it is only very close up that this looks a little different. This, because the area there right above the 9:00 position was designed with a break in the pattern of stones, which I'm guessing is some kind of artifact of the manufacturing process.

Similarly, at the top of the pendant, there are a few \\"empty\\" prongs, and again from a medium distance, it just looks like a continuation of the row of diamonds, only becoming gradually smaller.

I'm not sure what the pink plating is made of - both in terms of the metal and the colorant - but I do know that platings can wear off, so wouldn't suggest wearing this in the shower or on a ten mile hike...

I2-I3 is decidedly included, but the small size of individual stones and the cut makes the most of these. I really suspect that some of these stones are better than I2, and I'm not sure if that's a good or bad thing. (Again, it's a matter of little distinction as the necklace is viewed, but under a magnifier I could swear that some stones are brighter/sparklier than others.)

The chain is delicate enough for the pendant (serpentine or something like that would just look chunky by comparison), but it's a good 1MM plus in diameter so not particularly prone to knots.

If you like this, there is a matching ring and earring set: [[ASIN:B00TUMH7XM Sterling Silver White Diamond with Pink Plating Ring (1/3cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)]] and [[ASIN:B00TUMBBHA Sterling Silver White Diamond with Pink Plating Earrings (1/3cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)]]. I haven't seen either of these up close to vouch for them, but I do really love the design as it is in the pendant.ividual stones and the cut makes the most of these. I really suspect that some of these stones are better than I2, and I'm not sure if that's a good or bad thing. (Again, it's a matter of little distinction as the necklace is viewed, but under a magnifier I could swear that some stones are brighter/sparklier than others.)

The chain is delicate enough for the pendant (serpentine or something like that would just look chunky by comparison), but it's a good 1MM plus in diameter so not particularly prone to knots.

If you like this, there is a matching ring and earring set: [[ASIN:B00TUMH7XM Sterling Silver White Diamond with Pink Plating Ring (1/3cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)]] and [[ASIN:B00TUMBBHA Sterling Silver White Diamond with Pink Plating Earrings (1/3cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)]]. I haven't seen either of these up close to vouch for them, but I do really love the design as it is in the pendant.

product_title: MAZU Pearl Zircon-Accented Pendant Necklace AA+ Quality Top016 Color Rose Gold
review_headline: Gorgeous pendant, but the chain leaves much to be desired.
review_body:
I ordered this necklace to go with another product made by MAZU. The shipping was fast on the item, so I received it in a timely manner. When I took it out of the packaging, I was a bit disappointed that it didn't come with a nice necklace box to go with it. The pendant is very pretty, and the rose color accents pretty much any outfit, but the chain itself was a bit disappointing. The chain was a bit on the short side, in my opinion. Personally, I like necklaces like this to hang a bit lower. The chair itself felt flimsy. Because of this, I will likely purchase a difference chain to go with it, to really bring out the personality of the pendant. I adore the pendant itself. It's beautiful, detailed and has just enough sparkle for my taste.

I received this product at a discounted cost, in exchange for an honest review.

product_title: Sterling Silver 1.2mm Round Box Chain (14, 16, 18, 20, 22, 24, 30 or 36 inch)
review_body: For the last 15 years I've been wearing the simple white gold box chain that my Nonna gave me for my baptism. I wore it almost every day, changing out the charm. A few weeks ago it went missing. I tried wearing some of the necklaces that have come with my charm purchases, but I didn't like any of them. Finally gave up waiting to find my chain and went looking for a replacement. I didn't know what 1.1 mm looked like, but based on the reviews I decided to give it a try. I was pleasantly surprised, though I wish I had gotten something a little thicker - maybe 1.5 mm. I specifically didn't want to get a traditional box chain in case I find my old one, and opted for this round box chain. I really like it. It has a nice feel to it. One of my biggest peeves about necklaces is when they catch all the baby hairs on your neck, and this one does not do that. Great chain for a great price.

product_title: EleQueen Women's Crystal Princess Crown Tiara Party Adjustable Stacking Ring
review_headline: THIS GORGEOUS CROWN RING WOULD BE PERFECT FOR YOUR PRINCESS
review_body:
This is such a pretty and feminine ring. The rose gold champagne color and the crown shape make it unique and I truly love it. The costume ring is full of shine as it has Austrian crystal placed on the crown part. If you are not familiar with jewelry crystals, Austrian crystals are the coveted crystals, they sparkle so much more than lesser quality ones. The crown setting is intricate and with the crystals shiny, the ring looks very expensive. I have worked with and collected costume jewelry for over twenty five years, not to sound boastful but I have the knowledge to know the difference between low quality and high quality costume jewelry. This ring by EleQueen is definitely a better quality. I inspected the ring closely and all the of the shiny crystals are present and set tight. There are no rough or uncomfortable bulky edges to aggravate you while you have it on. The inside is polished very smooth. This ring is adjustable because of the small open place on band. This ring is very pretty, I would feel great wearing it with jeans and boots or with a sundress. It has great style and is sure to be noticed.
Another thing I would like to make note of is the pretty packaging that the ring was placed in. It comes in a swirly Tiffany blue gift box and tucked inside is also a pretty pink velvet pouch. So if you are buying this for a gift, it will be ready upon arrival.

product_title: Cute Orange Enamel Rhinestone Owl Silver Tone Long Necklace
review_body:
This is so cute. I found it to be a well made piece of costume jewelry. The Owl is adorable and measures about 2 inches high. His head moves and the back isn't solid to make the piece lighter. The jewels on his, are in well, not loose. The colors of the owl are bright and cover the whole owl. I did not see any bare spots. It is well painted enamel. It's a good price for such a well made piece. The chain is nice and decorative. The clasp is easy to close and stays shut.

Overall, I found this to be a well made piece of jewelry. It is cute and will add flair to any outfit. It would make the perfect gift for the owl lover in your life.

Note: I was offered this at a discount in exchange for my fair, honest, and unbiased opinion. It had no bearing on my review. I tested this thoroughly and formed my own opinions.

product_title: Black Acrylic Fake Cheaters Faux Illusion Plugs 4G Gauge 5mm 1 Pair Smallest
review_headline: Like a grave, IM DIGGIN' IT!
review_body: Ordered the 4 Gauge, 5mm faux plug in August of 2015.    From other reviews on similar faux plugs I read that the rubber gasket which is imbedded within the earring tends to slip out of it's housing. So, to deter this action from happening, I applied super glue to the end of a toothpick and carefully spread the glue in the crevices of the earring, and quickly replaced the rubber ring. Even through repeated washes after use, gasket has remained in place.     The bar of the earring is just a tad, slightly larger than your standard earring. The earring went in smoothly as a regular earring on the right, but my left piercing took about 4 minutes of patients and work to push through.     I ordered the 5mm because I wanted something that was not too large on the lobe, but looks decent and sharp. As it turns out, it was the perfect size and look I was hoping for!  _________________________________________________________    (Edit: 5-18-16)    After the first month of usage. I noticed that my lobes became bloated, red, and would also spell out a clear liquid after taking them out. I thought perhaps it was because my hole was adjusting to the slightly bigger bar. So, I let it run its course. But, after 8 months of usage, and the hole stretched to the bar size after about a month or so, my lobes would still get swollen, red, and still ooze the clear liquid which obviously is not a sign of adjusting, but an allergic reaction to the steel bar. I have even had a sort of whiteheads which have surfaced on both lobes from time to time after constant usage which has never, ever happens before. I have had my ears pierced since I was in the 5 grade and am now in my mid thirties, and I have never had my ears infected due to earrings which I have purchased at local jewelry shops. So most definitely assuming that the metal used in these earrings are not genuine, stainless steel.     I still use them every now and then, but I always immediately take them off after an outing and do not leave them on for overnight periods.    Had to drop my rating from 5 stars to 2. Hope you have different results such as I!
