product_title: Premium Sparkling Crystal Hematite Magnetic Bracelet - Healing for Joint Pain, RSI, Carpal Tunnel and Migraines
review_body:
I recently purchased this lovely little bracelet during a promotional period in exchange for my honest opinion. I am an avid crocheter and typist, and experience wrist pain when I have been working too much. I also suffer from migraine headaches at least 2-3 times per month. I don't always like to take medication, so I figured that this bracelet would be a good option for me.

I was very impressed with the presentation box. It was very cute, and would be nice if you are giving this bracelet as a gift. The bracelet itself is absolutely gorgeous. I've worked in direct sales with jewelry in the past, and this bracelet both fits my style and also fits in with some of the jewelry I already own. I love the colors of the faceted crystals, and the little hematite magnet beads don't give it the look of something "therapeutic;" it just looks like a fashionable piece of jewelry! It stretches to fit the wrist, but it doesn't give the feeling like it will stretch out or go slack easily, which I appreciate as well. It should fit nicely for a long time!

I haven't worn this bracelet every day, but when I do wear it, I notice that my wrist doesn't feel as tight (my right wrist tends to be worse than my left), and I'm able to crochet or type for longer periods of time without discomfort. I haven't had a migraine or sinus headache lately (knock on wood), but I fully intent to try out this little beauty when I do to see if it helps!

product_title: Hip Mall Punk Goth Metal Skull Pendant Chain Leather Choker Collar Necklace
review_headline: Gotten for a costume, kept because I fell in love!
review_body:
I am a Halloween person. To the point that I rather embarrass my children. So, when I saw this, I thought it would work in perfectly with the sexy vampire costume I was working on. It totally does! That's not the end of it, though, I was wearing a low cut dress when I first tried it on (not in front of a mirror at the time) and my husband turned to look at me and said that it was just what the dress needed. I kind of laughed because it was a navy blue plunge neck dress that flows down to the top of my feet and I couldn't imagine it being complimentary.

Being a woman, I didn't take his word for it. I went into our bedroom and looked in the full lenth mirror. Lo and behold, not only was it a perfect fit (but also adjustable by the snaps in the back), it really did look awesome with what was just a very plain, no frills, but flattering cotton dress. I have since found a few other outfits I have that it complements very well. This will continue to be well loved and well used.

For those of you looking for "that" kind of collar, because it is a regular snap in the back, I would tell you to be mindful that it's not meant to meet much resistance or stand up to much more than a small tug. If you want "that" kind of collar just for the aesthetic, this one is awesome. Somehow manages to be pretty, sexy, dangerous and delicate all at the same time. It really is leather, also, so if you have overly sensitive skin, I would recommend a leather softener/conditioner around the edges. I don't find an issue with it, but it IS bit on the raw side. I'm very happy with it and so glad that it can, will and has already served more than a costume accessory purpose. I'll be keeping a look out for other things Hip Mall might have coming out with in the near future.

*I RECEIVED THIS ITEM AT A DISCOUNT IN EXCHANGE FOR MY HONEST, FAIR AND UNBIASED REVIEW. ALL OPINIONS ARE MY OWN. I HAVE IN NO WAY BEEN COMPENSATED FOR MY REVIEW BY THE MANUFACTURER, DISTRIBUTOR OR ANY OTHER ENTITY ASIDE FROM SAID DISCOUNT, DISTRIBUTOR OR ANY OTHER ENTITY ASIDE FROM SAID DISCOUNT

review_headline: Fantastic, but I keep hearing voices...
review_body:
I ordered this ring as I've always wanted a One Ring of my very own. It arrived in a nice box, and it fit my finger very nicely. It definitely has a good weight to it, feels solid and well-made and the inscriptions are visible in the light, though they are difficult to see in less than bright conditions. Only downside to this is every time I put it on, I get transported to a strange dimension where everything is all hazy and I feel like I'm invisible. Its weird; plus every time I'm taken there, a giant eye of flame keeps appearing and speaking in a strange language. Plus, a wizard with a tall pointy hat and grey beard came to my house and kept asking me if it was secret and if it was safe.

Apart from those woes, it is a fantastic ring and I would highly recommend it. My...precious.

product_title: Knot Theory Silicone Wedding Rings Bands for Men Women in Silver, Gold, Grey, Blue - Non-bulky Band by Award-winning Designer - Best Quality, Style, Safety, Comfort - Ideal for Travel, Work, Exercises
review_headline: Why didn't someone think of this a long time ago???
review_body:
Ok, I have worked in a couple of fields, one where I sit at a desk all day, one on board a ship working with machinery, and one working with weapons and ammo and helicopters. Most of my jobs necessitated the taking off of my wedding band at one point or another. I lost one in Afghanistan on day 2, I lost one in California day 1 of vacation, and I lost one in a cabaret. This ring is awesome, it is perfect, it's so light I forget it's there, but it's snug enough not to fall off. I've honestly forgotten it's there and felt guilty for not having my ring on, only to look down and see it right there.

If you work with your hands, if you are forgetful, if you are allergic to precious medals ( I don't know :/ ) Get this ring! Cheap, tough, and takes a beating.

review_body: It really takes a lot for me to give a bad review. This was not an item I purchased at discount in exchange for an honest review. I bought this solely on my own. The bracelet is very cute. Adorable in fact. However, I only was able to wear this one time and it broke. My husband tried to fix it, but to no avail. I was sad because this was such a great concept, but failed in the actual production of the bracelet. It needed to be made with better materials to withstand the wearing around a person's wrist. Which obviously will be exposed to many underlying situations because it's on your arm! So regretfully, I have to give it two stars, the design is flawed, the concept is beautiful, but without honest criticism an inventor is not going to go far. I hope this helps the inventor reassess the making of this bracelet, make improvements and try again. Because I do love the overall idea.

product_title: Mens Silicone Wedding Rings Wedding Bands - 5 Pack, 4 Pack & 3 Pack - 8.7mm Wide (2mm Thick)
review_headline: Great for the spouse that works with their hands I ...
review_body:
Great for the spouse that works with their hands
My husband..boy do I love that man. I have to keep saying it just to remind myself at times. He does a lot of work with his hands, and even though I carefully and painstakingly picked out his Platinum wedding band with the fact that he likes to tinker with remote control cars and build various weird things with our in mind; he still feels the need to take it off when he is doing these things and usually losses or drops or a bear eats it.
We have gotten numerous "stand in" rings but they either cut into his finger because of the material or looked plain horrible as a stand in. So we tried a different approach and went for silicone. The Silicone Wedding Rings by ThunderFit is true to size and a very comfortable fit. It gives the symbolic meaning of "he is taken" but also of "yep I lost my ring again" . The ring withstood all of his manly activities and still was cute enough to be worn outside of the house and around town without looking like a crazy person and didn't turn his fingers any colors like the alternatives he tried to get himself.
Because it is a multi pack, I decided to use one when I went to the gym. It was very comfortable and I was still able to grip the machines like I am used to and didn't have to use the gloves. The ring was easy to put on and off and was easy to move when my hand was slightly swollen due to a weight dropping on it.
I received this item at a discounted price for my honest and unbiased review.

product_title: JoinMe Women's Punk Crystal Hollow-Out Wide Rock Bracelet Cuff Bangle Beaded Bling Gold-Tone
review_headline: Beautiful Bracelet, Love The Packaging Too!........... See Photos~
review_body:
The folks at JoinMe were kind enough to provide me with this product in exchange for sharing my unbiased review...

Surprisingly beautiful! I thought this bracelet might look a bit cheap or gaudy but was happy upon arrival to find I was wrong! Arrived in a pretty mint green gift box and an even nicer matching velvet jewelry bag! This would make a really cute gift!

They even included an extra two tiny crystals for in case any fall out. I thought this was a really nice unexpected touch and wish more costume jewelry did this!

Uploading some photos so you can get a better look. I have tiny wrists and inspite of it's large size, neither my husband or myself thought it looked too big for me. I also wear a chunky style watch. If you're wanting dainty, this isn't it, but if you like a statement peice, this is a good basic to add to your collection!

I might run a thin coat of some clear nail polish over the little crystals to ensure they stay in place but they do look fine as is. (Just from experience with these types of tiny gems, since I've lost some before.)

I think it would also fit a larger wrist comfortably as well. This type of bangle style is personally my favorite because they go off and on so easily. I especially like this one because you don't have to flex or bend it to put it on.

Who doesn't hate green wrists? Lol I have sensitive skin... This doesn't make me itch right off so that's a good sign! Seems like a 5 star item to me, excellent value, but I'll update this review after some use, regarding how it holds up. Hope this is helpful!

product_title: Gold Body Chain for Women, Ultra Strong Active Lifestyle Prime Quality Body Chain
review_body:
I really love this body chain. Not only because it is in style and is fun, but because you can attach it in different ways to create completely different looks using the same chain! I attached some images below of the looks that I've used this for (including as a body chain). It has two strings with a gold loop and two with the clips, so you can arrange them and clip them how you want to convey a certain look! Just be careful because it does tangle easily (since there are four loose and long chains coming from the main center piece. I've just been enjoying creating new ways to wear this body chain to get the most use out of it. The chain itself is really light too, so it doesn't weigh you down during the day like other longer necklaces do. I really enjoy this necklace! :)

*I received this product complimentary to test and give my honest and unbiased review*

product_title: 14K White Gold Round Solitaire Cubic Zirconia Engagement Ring, 1.5ct
review_headline: Not too big, not too small...just right.
review_body: I received this ring yesterday, and it is very pretty.  My engagement ring, which I now wear on my right hand, is a vintage-style halo ring, and it does not look great next to my plain, narrow wedding band. I wanted something that would fit against my wedding band without a gap.  This ring does just that.  I'm unable to confirm the 14K stamp they say is inside the band, but it appears to be white gold.  I ordered a size 6, and it fits perfectly. The center stone is slightly over 6mm, and each of the eight channel set side stones is 2mm. The setting stands 1/4" tall from my finger. When considering this ring, keep in mind that the setting will look larger on a smaller hand, something that is apparent from photos posted in various customer reviews.

product_title: Tribal Tibet Silver Grape Cluster Scale Pendant Bib Choker Collar Necklace
review_headline: A good value, but short of a five star quality
review_body:
I had high hopes for this necklace, despite it's price. It is attractive, though the way it was put together some of the "hardware" behind the scenes shows. On the necklace we received, on the right side, the layers are not as close in the picture and you can see the rings that hold it together through the gap. That being said, the necklace is still attractive and my wife likes it. For the price I am not terribly surprised, but it would be five stars without the visual appearance resulting from poor construction.

One note, the "leaves" are not all individual, but are connected in rows. It doesn't move as though they were all separate pieces, if that's something you're looking for.

I got this bracelet at a great price so I figured I had nothing to lose if I didn't like it. I'm glad it turned out that way.

It fits well, not too loosely, even for someone with small wrists such as myself.
The bracelet was lighter than I expected it to be, so the durability of the materials used may be of concern later, but initial quality appears good.
What I don't like about it is that, to me, it looks a bit feminine (decide for yourself).

Overall, it is of good initial quality, but I won't be keeping it. Likely will become a gift for my sister.

product_title: 14k Rose Gold Plated Sterling Silver Diamond (1/7 cttw) Infinity Pendant Necklace, 18"
review_body: I love the shape and size of the pendant. It is artistically unique with pretty stones on one side and the shiny gold on the other. My concern is the chain. It is very thin and fragile. It knots easily and takes a long time to untangle because you have to be so careful. I'm definitely replacing the chain. I give it wearing it one or two times before it breaks. Of course, it is made in China so it is not going to be an expensive gift. If you want something pretty and dainty, it is a good choice. Just plan on replacing the chain. The pendant has several holes to loop a new one through and is thicker, making it much more sturdy. I believe the longevity of the pendant and stones is fairly good.

product_title: BeOne®2015 New Antique Silver Color Six disc Joint Pizza Slice Friendship Necklace Set (Five Piece Set)
review_body:
This is a one slice piece of pie necklace. Or, if you work for me work, this is a one slice piece of pizza pendant on a necklace.

I have no idea why it makes me hungry for a salad, but maybe it's because I don't eat pizza. But, when I handed this necklace over to a teenager, she thought it was the cutest thing in the whole wide world. She couldn't wait to run across the street to go show her brothers and sisters. I thought that was super cute.

Necklace is a bow the perfect size and link for a teenager, and the little slice of pizza, even though I think it looks a little funny, it was loved by a teen. This would actually be really cool for teenagers to get the whole pie, that way you can give little slices of pizza to your friends. To get the whole pie you would have to get six and that's not a horrible idea. Again. I think it would be perfect for a group of friends.

So, I would recommend this to teenagers, two parents and teenagers, or to anyone who knows a group of kids that would think this was adorable.

I received this product at a discounted rate for an honest review.

product_title: Love You More Spinner Ring - Stainless Steel Ring - Love Ring - Commitment Jewelry
review_headline: Telephone "good-byes" and a tribute to my sister.
review_body: Aug 12, 2016---update---My heart isbreaking b/c I lost this ring when I fell down a flightof stairs.  My heart justbreaks b/c I lost this cherished ring.  I will purchase another one  .    I wanted to share my story of this ring. Whenever my sister and I would speak on the phone, as we were concluding our conversation, she would always say "love you  more", then I would repeat back to her, and we would banter back and forth. I purchased this for my sister Christmas 2014.  When she received it, she was very happy, not only with the gift, but also with the quality and "look" of the ring.  Once she received the ring, she never took it off....until the day she passed away this year......July 30th. When she started to "go down hill", I stayed with her (we live about 1.5 hours apart) and helped her husband take care of her.  She had several admits to hospitals then back home, then back to the hospital.  During this time, her husband and I were with her. Whether she was at home or in the hospital, she would point to the ring and tell me "...love you more..." and the usual banter ensued.  I would lay in the bed with her and we would watch Gunsmoke or some other show, not saying anything.....because this Ring said it all.  No other words were needed.  The last day/time I saw her, she was being admitted back to the hospital.  She was put in the ambulance, doors were shut, and I ran to the back of the ambulance just in time and shouted through the doors, "....LOVE YOU MORE!", to which she responded with a hand/finger gesture (non-verbally) as if to say-- "...uh uh,,,,love you more". I am so glad I found this ring on your site. Because of  our telephone conclusions of "love you more"....,, your ring became a special heirloom signifying something so sweet and precious to us----something so great that it "took on a life of its own". For the special "gift" your ring gave us, I sincerely thank you.  Those words"love you more" that I was able to speak to her the last time I saw her are forever in our hearts and on my finger!  Thank you.  S. Campbell

product_title: SOUFEEL Swarovski Crystal Camera Charm 925 Sterling Silver Charms Fit European Bracelets
review_headline: A great retro-like camera charm that's perfect for the photograph buff ...
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:8dd4997dcd2cf577292d4c420c7022c4]]This is one of the Soufeel charms that many people can relate to, whether they are amateur photographers or pros. Of course what makes it shine is that Swarovski crystal that is right smack dab where the lens would be. It's really a cute charm, but I didn't realize what it was until I looked closely. These charms can be worn either on Pandora or Chamilia bracelets, but not the old-fashioned style of charm bracelet. Simply select your starter bracelet and begin to collect. They can also be worn on a simple sterling chain if desired.

Many people obviously are selecting charms that do have meaning to the wearer obviously this is one that will appeal to the photo nut. The Swarovski crystal has that unmistakable glint that all of their crystals have. There's no mistaking it for a piece of cubic zirconium or a bit of cut glass. The camera does have a retro-like look to it and reminds me of when everyone used to be into learning about taking proper shots rather than doing the simple point and shoot bit. I had a charm bracelet as a young girl, but the charms I've seen from Soufeel are infinitely more detailed and appealing. The bracelets and charms are now coming back into vogue with the advent of the Pandora.

FEATURES:

‚ñ∫ .925 Sterling Silver

‚ñ∫ Diameter: 5 millimeters

‚ñ∫ Compatible with Pandora and other main brand bracelets (unthreaded)

I've seen a lot of charms and the high-quality materials and craftsmanship are evident in the Soufeel charms I have. This foundation of these charms is sterling silver and is marked .925. The detailing is lovely and it's quite obvious that these are special charms for special occasions. They do come with velvet-like drawstring bags that work well for gift-giving or for storage.

Sample provided for review.

product_title: Bamoer 18k Rose Gold Snowflake Crystal Pendant Necklace Anniversary Gift for Women
review_body:
Rose-toned items are quite popular now, and I was quite happy to accept this free item for evaluation and review as I wear this color a lot with my beige, brown, and pink clothing items. This is a snowflake pendant with cubic zirconia and it is about 1/2 inch in diameter. The chain is a simple interlocking type that culminates in a series of larger metal chain pieces so that you can adjust the length as desired with a maximum length of about 18 inches. This length hits me about midchest and it is the length I prefer when wearing lower cut dresses and tops. I believe this would look lovely as an accent accessory for any woman or older teen girl.

The necklace came in a plastic bag and you might want to transfer it to a fancier box if you are giving it as a gift, but it is very pretty and has a lovely sparkle that catches the light. It is simple and elegant.

review_headline: I did not get a good product with this
review_body: I did not get a good product with this, it is cheap but it had some problems. The first is that it did not come with sizes 10g and 8g. So i jumped from a 12 to a 6. I had no problem with that but that came with another issue. The double flared gauges that came with the 6g were not the same size so i streched a 6 taper to a 4 double flare without noticing. Some may say that is my fault and i did over look that, but if a product is separated by baggies it would be safe to assume that the flares are the same as the taper that is in the SAME BAGGY. The other unfortunate thing about this product that i received is that the baggies are not labeled, and since it did not come with the 10g-8g i had to guess what sizes they were. So a summary is i did not get a complete product and they were not organized in their "organized" separator bags.

product_title: 14g 16mm (5/8 Inch) Hypoallergenic PTFE Flexible Ultra Glitter Nipple & Tongue Ring Barbell
review_headline: Once you go Bio-Flex you never go back  =P
review_body:
I absolutely love this tongue ring! the ONLY reason I gave it four stars is because of the price. For one single tongue ring, the price is up there. But the product itself I would give 5 stars.

I've had my tongue pierced for a few years but this is only the second bio flex tongue ring I have purchased. The last one lasted about a year or so, and I do chew/ bite on it quite a bit when I'm bored or nervous kinda like someone who chews on their nails. My point being it tok a lot of wear and tare before it finally broke. its made pretty sturdy but still has the flexibility that I love and won't damage your teeth like one with a metal bar.

It's much more comfortable than a metal bared tongue ring. Because it is so light, its not bothersome at all either. This is 5/8 of an inch which is shorter than what you get when you first get it pierced which is usually a 7/8 of an inch. I would not recommend this tongue ring for someone who has recently gotten their tongue pierced, you need to leave the metal one in until your tongue has healed. As soon as it was healed I would switch it right out to one of these. I don't even understand why people continue to wear the metal ones after the healing time. I wish more people knew about bio-flex rings; because once you go Bio-Flex, you never go back ;D

product_title: SOUFEEL Red Travel Suitcase Charm 925 Sterling Silver Charms Fit European Bracelets Women Gift
review_headline: A great retro-like red suitcase that's perfect for the person who has been or is going on a special trip ...
review_body:
[[VIDEOID:cba9116c40fd46d635a8df9e681b109e]]This Soufeel charm is a great retro-like one of a travel case from decades ago. Just holding it in my hands reminds me of trips I took years ago. Probably anyone who has had a memorable trip would love to have this particular charm. It had a great `look' and is marvelously detailed. I especially like the overlay of red, something that makes it a standout charm. These charms can be worn either on Pandora or Chamilia bracelets, but not the old-fashioned style of charm bracelet. Simply select your starter bracelet and begin to collect. They can also be worn on a simple sterling chain if desired.

When I was a youngster I had a charm bracelet, but apart and aside from one's birthstone charm, most of them had no meaning. Many people are now selecting charms that have meaning to the wearer and obviously this one is for someone who has taken or will be taking a special trip. I have several Soufeel charms and they are all high-quality ones that I wouldn't hesitate to purchase or recommend. They are very detailed and quite appealing. The bracelets and charms are now coming back into vogue with the advent of the Pandora.

FEATURES:

‚ñ∫ .925 Sterling Silver

‚ñ∫ Diameter: 5 millimeters

‚ñ∫ Compatible with Pandora and other main brand bracelets (unthreaded)

I've seen a lot of charms and the high-quality materials and craftsmanship are evident in the Soufeel charms I have. This foundation of these charms is sterling silver and is marked .925. The detailing is lovely and it's quite obvious that these are special charms for special occasions. They do come with velvet-like drawstring bags that work well for gift-giving or for storage.

product_title: EleQueen Women's Gold-tone Cream Simulated Pearl Long Ball Dangling Double Dangle Earrings Ivory Color
review_headline: Very easy to put on, and quite light and comfortable.
review_body:
Free product provided for evaluation and review.

These are cute and comfortable. They are VERY easy to put on. Each pearl slips off. I took the largest part off and threaded it through my ear front to back, it really could not have been easier. They do have little posts closures in with the set, if you want to use them, but I have not seen a need for it. Once in and the pearls are slid back into place, everything stays where it is supposed to. The simulated pearls have a very nice, realistic lustre to them and look like good quality beads.
They are light and don't weigh a lot by my scales just 4.55 grams each.
They come in a cute little gift box with a little pink velvet drawstring bag, so they make a nice presentation if you wanted to give them as a gift.
They are quite simple costume fashion pieces, but they are pleasant to wear and look nice.
Pictures pending.

product_title: Amazing Silver Blue Iced Out Paved Hummingbird Fashion Pendant Mood Necklace Jewelry Gift for Women Girls
review_headline: Hummingbird lover in my house is one happy girl with this necklace!
review_body:
For the hummingbird lovers..this is a cute necklace.

It is actually better than I was expecting. It has a nicer quality to it and appears to be well made.

The silver chain is adjustable from 15 - 18 inches and the bird is made from a Rhodium plated base with rhinestones and crystals.

It would make a cute gift for a young lady. Nice enough to wear but not something you would get too upset if they misplaced it. My daughter loves hummingbirds and she called dibs on this as soon as it arrived earlier today. The chain is nice and because it is adjustable, it can be worn at different drop levels.

Overall this is a nice piece of jewelry that won't must the bank. Would make a nice gift or stocking stuffer. It can be stored in the velvet bag that came with it for safe keeping and protection.

A few people have mentioned that the gold is not as yellow as in the photos... It IS a little lighter, but I still find it a nice accent. I took pictures of it, and my camera washes out the gold, making it look paler than it does in person.

Finally got so frustrated I just bent them up, which was increily easy since they were so thin and cheap, and threw them away.  Do NOT buy these!!

product_title: Best Friends Locket Necklace- Charm Locket Friendship Love Gift BFF Fashion Jewelry
review_headline: Truly a High Quality Magnetic Floating Charms Locket with Back Plate, Charms, Crystals and 22" Chain!
review_body:
This Best Friends Floating Charms Locket by A Touch Of Dazzle is Too Cute!
The 1 1/8" Round Stainless Steel Locket can be Opened to Add or Change the charms and features a Strong, 4 Magnet Closure to assure it won't open without assistance.
The Back Plate Is Silver and is Etched in Black with the Words "Best Friends" and Two Intertwining Open Hearts.
Inside the Locket are 4 Sparking Crystals in Dark Pink, Green, Yellow and Blue, as well as Three 1/4" Colorful, Metal Charms.
The Charms in mine include a White Heart which says "Friends" and has a Small White Flower and a Brightly Colored Pink Star on it; A Pink, Dark Blue and White "Rainbow and Clouds" Charm and a Pretty Flower Charm with Pink and Yellow "Petals", as well as a Small Clear Crystal in the Center of the Flower.
The Upper Rim of the Locket is a Lovely Pink Color and both the Front and Back of the Charm are Clear Glass. The Rim on the Back as well as the sides of the Locket are a Polished Stainless Silver.
This Charm has a Solid, Well Set Hinge, so no worries of it coming apart no matter how many times it is opened and closed.
The Bale is Securely Soldered to the Locket and offers plenty of room for the 22" Stainless Steel Rolo Chain to pass through.
The Rolo Chain features an Easy to Manipulate Lobster Claw Clasp on one end and an 18 Link Chain Extender for easy length adjustment on the other.
A Touch Of Dazzle ships this adorable Locket/Necklace in a Shiny Pink Gift Box with a Satin Ribbon and Bow attached to the top of the box.
I was given the opportunity to receive mine at a reduced cost in exchange for testing and review and will be gifting it to my niece for her 14th Birthday. I have no doubt she is going to love it as much as I do!
Truly a High Quality Magnetic Floating Charms Locket with Back Plate, Charms, Crystals and 22" Chain and I am giving it my Highest Recommendation!

product_title: Sterling Silver Embossed Basket Weave Cuff Bracelet
review_body: This basket weave pattern is very intricate.  The overall look of the cuff bracelet is beautiful and stylish.  The feel of the bracelet is very light weight and thin...material wise.  I don't believe a moderate to large wrist would be a good fit.  The bracelet may pinch a bit and I don't think that would be very comfortable.  The cuff does open and give a little room but not much without the fear of damaging the bracelet.  I don't know how this braclet will wear in the long haul but it will probably be fine for a short haul. product_title: Stainless Steel Plain Wedding Band Ring 8mm Comfort Fit Sizes 6 Thru 14
review_body:
This ring is beautiful. I wanted a ring that was not so expensive but looked nice. This ring is perfect. I am very impressed with the comfort fit. The comfort fit just means that it's kind of rounded on the inside like it is on the outside. It makes a world of difference in the feel of the ring and definitely worth a try. I can't say that I've seen a ring at this price level with that feature.

This would make a great ring to wear on vacation, out of the country, on a trip of any kind, hiking, at the beach...anywhere you still want to wear a ring, but don't want to be wearing anything you can't afford to replace.

I would recommend this ring without reservation for use as a wedding, accent or thumb ring and is wide enough for a man or woman. I have this in 4MM and 8MM. I wear the 4MM with an anniversary ring and the 8MM alone. I would recommend this band in the 4MM.

product_title: Casoty Jewelry Star Trek Cufflinks Starfleet Command Cufflinks in Gift Box
review_headline: High Quality Metal Cufflinks! Painted Starfleet Logos! Comes in Baggie Requiring Unpack for Proper Gifting...
review_body:
I love Star Trek, although I wouldn't consider myself a "Trekkie" but I have seen all the TV shows, well, except for DS9, have not gotten around to that, but hopefully will some day soon! When I was given the opportunity to own a pair of Star Trek Cuff Links I figured, why not!?

The cuff links arrived in a little plastic baggie stuck inside a black jewelry box. So if you're buying this as a gift I would recommend opening it up, and putting the cuff links properly into the jewelry box for proper presentation. Honestly, that is the only real negative here, the fact that they didn't go the extra step to place these in the box properly. But to be fair to them, this probably saves a ton of money, which they have obviously passed on to the consumer, as the price is incredible for the quality, especially with it being Star Trek related, as that tends to always command a premium.

The actual link itself is about an inch long, and the Starfleet Logo is painted on metal. The paint looks durable, but I have not worn it enough to see how much abuse they can withstand. But honestly, how often are you going to wear them? Unless you're an executive that is in a suit, daily, you probably will only wear these a few times per year on special occasions. The fact that the logo is black and white is great as it means it will essentially match anything you pair it with. They are also light and are not noticeable at all when wearing them.

Overall, a high quality great product that I would recommend as a gift for any Trekkie in your life. Besides the need to properly unpack and present prior to gifting, and maybe the paint job being not as detailed as I'd like, it is a great gift! And really, no one is going to notice it unless they are literally several inches from it, and if they are that close to your wrists then, well, they are probably a close friend, and probably aren't going to be a jerk and call you out on petty details such as that.

DISCLAIMER: I was provided a sample unit by the company. I did not promise them a review but seeing as I used it, and I love to review things, I was more than happy to provide a fair review to help other users make an informed purchase.br />

review_headline: Awesome for a 12 year old girl's birthday gift
review_body:
Both my sister and I have necklaces with charms in them and my niece has shown interest in them and told me what charms she would get if she had one. I came across this necklace and knew that since her 12th birthday was coming up, this would be the perfect gift for her. It's something she can have in common with both her mom and I, but also something she can continue to add to as she grows older and her interests change.
The box it comes in is perfect for giving it as a gift which makes my life a lot easier. The photo shows me wearing it as her birthday isn't until November. I will update with new pics then. It has an adjustable chain so it can fit adults or children.
The charms were extremely cute and looked identical to the photo they were shown in which is amazing to me because they're so tiny, but perfectly shaped and painted! The chain quality was actually better than some chains I have that I paid more for, which is really impressive to me and means it can withstand a 12 year old girls handling!
I can't wait for her birthday now because I just know she will be beside herself with happiness and love!

product_title: BAMOER DIY European Style Love Heart Blue Crystal Murano Glass Bead Charms Fit Bracelets For Woman Girls 20CM 7.8"
review_body:
I absolutely love a "statement" bracelet, and this one is absolutely gorgeous for the price. It is quite heavy and feels like a very quality item when you remove it from the shipping bag. After I examined the beautiful charms -- lovely and unique in pink and green and pink and silver designs (you can see them quite clearly in the photographs on this product page), I tried to put it on! I was stymied as it appeared that one was to slide it up over the palm as there is no obvious clasp! A quick email to the great customer service representatives at Bamoer (I obviously should have looked at the product page and the other reviews more closely fist) reveals that there is a hidden clasp on the "LOVE" charm -- you put a fingernail in the slot and -- VOILA! it opens like magic! Closing it one-handed again with ease depends on your facility with the hand you're using, but I was able to capture the other end without any difficulty and secure the clasp. I noticed that some had remarked that the other charms could fall off while the clasp was undone, but I did not see this as an issue as there is a "stop" point that prevented the charm from coming up over the end. Don't be afraid to push hard!

I received this item for free for evaluation and review and can highly recommend it for anyone looking for a lovely accessory. It is suitable for all ages from teen to adult. It comes in a plastic bag, so if you're wanting to give it as a gift, you may want to transfer it to a more fancy gift box for the presentation. It is a very high quality and beautiful bracelet.

review_body:
I received this product in exchange for my honest opinion.

When I first received the product my impressions were that it was very nicely made.The ring arrived in a black bag and well packaged. I actually got this ring for myself because I tend to get my diamond ring stuck on everything. The finish on the ring makes it very smooth so it is perfect for anyone that works with their hands. The ring is not really thick at all which makes it perfect! The design is nice as well! It is a deep colored black with two silver rings around it. The script on the ring is very nicely printed, but is very hard to read. Don't expect others to be able to see what it is from any distance.

In all this is a very nice piece and I would recommend it to anyone looking for an alternative to their traditional wedding band or a diamond ring. I just love not having to worry about it getting caught on anything at all.

product_title: 18k Yellow Gold Plated Sterling Silver Two-Tone Filigree Cuff Bracelet, 7.25"
review_headline: Sturdy cuff-great piece of jewelry for weekly wear
review_body:
This bracelet is lovely, sturdy, and even a good price(right now at 70.) for 25 grams of 925 sterling silver and some gold plating.

It has a beautiful design, as pictured, with an interwoven silver and gold motif. The silver part has small reflective pieces that look similar to a diamond chips but are just design. It comes in a lovely box and I keep it in that box to keep it looking nice and new. I have had no problem so far with any color change. Since this is gold plated, the gold won't last forever, but the silver base will.

It is a nice thick bangle and can be squeezed smaller or expanded a little wider to fit your wrist. I initially wore it for a few hours and my niece did as well. We both found that the bracelet seemed almost unnoticeable as it was quite comfortable.

The style is fairly versatile and I found two pairs of earrings in my own collection that match great, both are from the Amazon collection. It adds a nice touch to many every day outfits.

product_title: Stainless Steel 1.0MM Rolo Cable Chain - (16" - 30" Available)
review_headline: and it seems like some other buyers noted the same shorter-than-expected length
review_body:
There is something wrong with this seller's chains. I ordered a 16" chain but it was 15", and it seems like some other buyers noted the same shorter-than-expected length. As for the quality of the chain, the link connecting to the clasp is thin, very slightly ajar, and doesn't seem all that strong, but the body of the chain is okay. I realized that several years ago I ordered chains from the same seller and they all were a bit shorter than they were supposed to be, but this particular chain was very noticeably shorter.

The seller did allow me to return the chain for free, but in the end I decided to keep it because I can tolerate the 15" chain, and it's not worth sending back a cheap chain, and I'm surmising they would've sent a replacement with the exact same wrong length anyway. Just note that whatever length you order may be an inch shorter, so be careful.

product_title: Sterling Silver Diamond Heart Pendant Necklace (1/10 cttw), 18"
review_headline: Clasp (lobster claw) is very hard to fasten
review_body: I just got this today and I love the style.  It is dainty with a very thin chain.  The diamonds are chips of course but they pave one side of the heart.  I would say that this is an elegant piece of jewelry.  This is actually the second piece of silver jewelry that I have gotten from Amazon and I have liked both.  The other necklace I got was also silver but it was thicker and slightly larger (more substantial).  The only thing I do not like is the lobster claw fastener on this necklace.  While I like a lobster claw and I feel they are more study and safer (less likely to come apart and lose the jewelry), this one is quite tiny and the opening for the claw part to go through is so small that it took me about 5 minutes of working at it to finally get it hooked so I could wear it.  I am thinking that I might have to change the claw or change the chain on the necklace as it is really that difficult to fasten.  That is the reason that I put this piece at 4 stars vs. 5.

product_title: Clear Crystal Magnet Stud Earrings Magnet Earring Unisex Men's Earring Clear--4 Claw
review_headline: Noticable Pain, Very Strong Magnets. Fashion is Pain, right?
review_body: Many have posted that these start to hurt your ears after a while of wearing and I agree. Those magnets are strong!  They are so strong, in fact, that a few times I have accidentally knocked these off my ears while pushing my hair back or brushing my hair, and when I go to pick them up, I find the magnet reattached on the fall down. I was able to comfortably wear them for a few hours. Thereafter, the pain became noticeably uncomfortable. To solve this I'd simply move them over a little on each ear throughout the night. They do have a costume appearance, but that was to be expected.  I also noticed that mine came with multiple magnets for each earring.  This was a nice perk, since the magnets are small and if you aren't careful you can drop them and never find them again.

product_title: Kennedy Competition V2 Style RDA (Stainless Steel)
review_headline: any RDA is great. Now if you are looking for maximum airflow ...
review_body:
Product is well made from Stainless Steel product. Fires and hits very well with very little problems. If doing your own coil builds, any RDA is great. Now if you are looking for maximum airflow then this is your RDA. There are 2 air flows from the top that flow into the RDA, along with 4 post air flows that come from the bottom into the RDA. Also features with a deep well to hold your cotton and juice. Cloud production varies on unit its used with, along side with juice quality and coil setup.

Some hazards to full-metal caps to RDA's is: Overheating from constant use (may cause burn to lips or inner mouth, along with other bodily parts). And electrical overheats, usually caused by the coils ends/tails to touch either cap, another wire/coil, or create a short electrical circuit by the coil touching more than two parts of either the positive or negative posts.

Intermediate to Expert Experience is required for any drip-system RDA's.
If you don't know how to use the product or know the product along with its side affects, please contact a local specialist (Vape Shop). They will be more than happy to help and get you on your way to enjoying your purchased product.

product_title: Lowpricenice(TM)Hot Turkish Jewelry Bohemian Ethnic Vintage Silver Coin Bracelet
review_body:
A little noisy for people working in a quiet office. It is adjustable to different size wrists. The clasp was a little stiff at first. There is a single disc at the end of the clasp so a tighter fit means a longer dangling coin - nice detail. Design is on both sides of the coin-like discs but only one-side of the triangle part where the adjustable chain part connects (coins do not go completely around wrist due to adjustable chain part). The metal, round beads are strung over the metal chain and it is connected to the other row every two round beads. Seven discs in all, including the one at the end of the clasp.

There is a lot of detail for the price. Wearers will have to careful of o-rings that connect as they are not fully closed in some places. I may just take some tweezers and fix this before wearing out. It was delivered 34 days before given arrival time.

product_title: Kenneth Cole New York "Delicates" Pave Circle Chain Front and Back Earrings
review_body: I don‚Äôt usually gravitate toward front-and-back earrings, but I was attracted to the Kenneth Cole ‚ÄúDelicates‚Äù Front-and-Back earrings because of the pave circles, which feel traditional while the chain gives them a kind of a rocker vibe. I thought these gold-toned Kenneth Cole earrings marry traditional and trendy well. The friction backs are attached by the 1-inch chain to the earrings so there‚Äôs no more misplacing or losing the backs, which sometimes happens with regular earrings.  They are very comfortable and light to wear.  The tiny crystals in the circles give these earrings their sparkle and the chains, hanging from the earlobes have a ‚Äúhoop-like earring‚Äù effect.  I wear them when I‚Äôm in the mood for something ‚Äúdifferent,‚Äù for something that it‚Äôs me and yet not quite me.  If you like conventional looks with a little edge, these earrings will do nicely.

product_title: 10k White Gold Diamond Twist Ring (1/10 cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)
review_headline: Great use of this quality of Diamond at a great price
review_body: This is a very nice promise ring.  When worn, it is very comfortable on the finger and lightweight.  The prongs are smooth and do not scratch or catch on clothing, unlike another ring that I own.  The 7 clustered diamonds in the center of the ring help give the smaller diamonds a larger appearance and the small diamonds "twisted" around the main cluster and extra prongs also give the illusion of a larger carat weight.  The color of the diamonds (I-J) is good and while these are listed with a high number of inclusions, because the diamonds are so small, you can't really see them with the naked eye.  The setting is set high off of the finger, giving this ring some height as well.  Overall, Amazon did a good job of making the best of what diamond size/cut/color/inclusions they were working with.  For a woman who prefers white gold to yellow, this "promise" should make her very happy.

product_title: Women Stainless Steel CZ Cubic Zirconia Eternity Ring for Wedding Band Engagement,7mm Width
review_body:
This ring is gorgeous and has a TON of shimmer! I actually purchased this exact ring from QVC some time ago, and sent it back because it was $30, and the crystals fell out. (Of course, if that happens with this one, I will be back to update my rating). I received this one free for review, so I am happy to give it a shot. So far, so good! It has four rows of crystals that sparkle like crazy, and I am definitely coming back for the pink, blue and green. I love this style, it's very smooth on the inside, and very comfortable to wear. I have a lot of jewelry, but stainless steel is my favorite because it never tarnishes, never irritates my skin, and is crazy tough! I started wearing it when my kids were born, because they were always yanking and being rough with my jewelry. I have never been disappointed with steel jewelry, and the price is always right! If you like a bold look, order more than one color and wear the together!! The ring doesn't come gift boxed; I put it in my own gift box because it's easier to photograph that way. I took a photo with the flash off, so you could see the detail of the ring, and another with the flash on, so you could see it sparkle.
Update: I am still wearing these frequently, and no crystals have fallen out. Excellent!
Update: The white one is still wearing perfectly, none of the stones have fallen out. I now have the green one, and love to wear them together! They don't snag on anything and are very comfortable to wear, sizing is perfect.

product_title: Womens Girls 18K Gold Plated Crystal Bib Statement Collars Necklace Pendant Jewelry with Chain
review_headline: Colorful and bold statement necklace; the crystals shimmer like real gemstones
review_body:
This necklace is big, colorful and bold. The crystals are cut well, they actually shimmer like gemstones-gorgeous! But they do shine less when you touch them, the fingerprints stick and you have to wipe it off. The backs are encased, not just painted like many cheaper necklaces. The necklace is 18" long with a 3" extender, so 21" total, with a big lobster claw clasp that is very easy to open and close. The largest pendant (center, green), has a 1.75" drop. I received this necklace free to review. It's honestly a bit too much necklace for me, but my friend works in the local newsroom and she went CRAZY for it, so I gave it to her. She adores bold statement necklaces, and wears them all-the-time (even to the grocery store! that woman is stylin' 24/7). The price for this necklace is out of this world-very affordable! I have seen her spend $60-$100 on (faux) crystal necklaces in a local 'boutique' that aren't as pretty as this one.

I had to update my review, and drop the stars, a lot! The first time she wore it, it just fell apart. The lobster claw clasp snapped off, and the extender broke off, allowing all the pendants to fall off. There was no fixing it, so I had a white leather cord, and we just strung one pendant on the cord, it's interchangeable at least. It can still be worn together or apart, but it's not as pretty as it was on the original necklace. I have uploaded the photos

product_title: Unique Handmade Jewelry Crystal Blue Donut Pendant Necklace
review_body:
Accessories can definitely make an outfit pop so choosing just the right one for my style of clothing is pretty important to me. This Unique Handmade Jewelry Crystal Blue Donut Pendant Necklace looked really nice when I ordered it but it's even more beautiful in person. It feels very well-made and the clasp is located on the front and is the type where you fit the long piece into the circle to make it stay. It blends in well with the design of the necklace. The necklace is 22 inches and fits me perfectly. The design is intricate and very well thought out. It's elegant and classy yet can be worn with both casual and dressy outfits. There's a tag on the necklace that says it's natural dumortierite and blue sponge coral. If not aware, and in case you are into crystals, dumortierite is a type of crystal that is suppose to help bring you to good places in life. An added bonus to this necklace is that it comes with a very beautiful gift bag so it can be given away to someone if wanted. Overall, I'm very impressed with this necklace and it has held up perfectly each time I've worn it.

I received this product for free so that I may test it out and write an honest, unbiased product review. All opinions expressed are truly my own.

product_title: 18k Rose Gold and Rhodium Plated Sterling Silver Diamond Accent Filigree Dangle Earrings (1/10cttw, I-J Color, I2-I3 Clarity)
review_headline: Do you want to look "Gor Geous" ??
review_body:
These are absolutely Gorgeous!
The rose gold sets off the diamonds that are embedded in them. These will definitely "POP" and be noticed whether you ahve light or dark colored hair. Mine is long dark brown and even when it partially obscures them you can see them sparkling as they catch the light as my head moves.

These are a nice weight, they feel substantial and well made,
They're VERY sparkly and pretty, the ear wires are also the rose gold so they have a very cohesive well planned appearance to them.

I looked up to see exactly what "Rhodium plating" is and pulled up this:
"Rhodium is a precious metal, a member of the platinum family. Rhodium electroplating is used, especially on jewelry, to provide a surface that will resist scratches and tarnish, and give a white, reflective appearance."

So the shiny, sparkly appearance should last and as a bonus I spotted a matching necklace to these earrings I'm going to be asking for my upcoming birthday!
OOOO I'm going to look sooo "Gor Geous"
LOL, *(a nod to Sandra Bullock in her role as Gracie in Miss Congeniality) ;-P

My love for animals combined with the perfect statement piece!

product_title: White Shark Charm Beads for Pandora Bracelet Charms Cheap 925 Sterling Silver Plated Jewelry New Sale
review_headline: Shark lovers need this bead for their bracelets!
review_body:
My three year old LOVES sharks, just like his mommy and grandfather, so I wanted this bead for my charm bracelet since sharks are so important to my family. It symbolizes both my father, who passed 15 years ago, and my son. Though they never met, I feel like this shared love brings them together, so this bead means a lot to me.

What I didn't realize from the photo is the shark is kind of turned, so the hole starts near the tail and the bracelet actually goes through the mouth. I thought the whole went side to side and the shark's head would be in the front of the bracelet, so this was a nice surprise. I love the look of the shark eating the bracelet! This fit perfectly on my Chamilia bracelet. It's bright and shiny and goes well with my other beads. It does screw on so it's perfect for the end of my bracelet as it keeps other beads from sliding off.

The jewelry ships from China so it is a little slow, however I received it much quicker than expected - a week before the first date in the estimate, almost a month before the end date. I am very happy with this purchase and will post updates if anything changes. This item was received at a discount in exchange for an honest, unbiased review.

product_title: INBLUE Men's Stainless Steel Ring CZ Silver Tone Black Red Cross Knight Fleur De Lis Oval
review_headline: This ring is mediocre due to the non-metallic parts
review_body:
Get the ring to your actual ring size. Don't listen to anyone who says otherwise. They don't know what their ring sizes are. I took a keyring and used it to size my fingers, most of them fit easily, some had a squeeze. I measured, went to a legitimate chart, and ordered. The rings fit (four of them, all different, not even same brand). I will say this, don't order up. If you measure a 12 or think the size chart listed for the rings is a bit to the far end, get the smaller size. I have muscular and squat fingers, they fit fine for me at the larger end, especially when flexed.

This is my least favorite of the four rings I bought. I would picture a religious role player type wearing this, perhaps a pope or semi-important figure. It is quite a stand out piece. The red inlay on mine, however, looks fractured.... as if it might break loose and fall out at any moment. I can't really say that close scrutiny would hold up for this item, not that you expect a masterpiece for the price. From a few feet it likely works fine, but from personal distances it will fail you, at least in my case. I may purchase the black inlay and see if that serves me better, though red is my favorite.

product_title: CrazyPiercing Taper Stretching Guages Kit with Acrylic Plug Kit
review_headline: decent set but slightly off in sizing.
review_body: These definitely do the trick but I will say they are all a tad bit smaller than the plugs or tapers you would buy at say hot topic or other stores I have had my ears stretched for 10 years and got a random but crazy infection in my right lobe due to having an infected tooth pulled but I had to take out jewelry and my Dr had to make a tiny incision to get the lobe to drain therefore my ear had closed up pretty well and I went from a 00 to a 8g in aprox 2 weeks or so and I must have lost my orginal tapers from sizes 4g-0g and I was afraid of getting another infection or ripping the lobe by going from a lobe size 6g to a 00 taper so I bought these since the price was right and reviews we're decent again they all came sorted in individual bags and every taper and plug is here but be careful using these to stretch then trying to put a plug of the same size into your ears I have gotten up to the 0g in this pack but my 0 gauge plugs will not fit they are too big for my ear but the 0g plug and taper from this set is what I have in now and my 00g tapers are bigger by a hair then the ones in this package. So again this is a good set for the price just please be careful with what you try to put into your lobes when using these to stretch. I would almost say they are each a size smaller than what they are suppose to be. But again I don't feel like it's a whole size smaller but 100% they are in between sizes from orginal all tapers I have from 14g-6g and my 00g none of these are the exact size as the ones I have owned for 10 years I bought all my original tapers from hot topic and Spencers gifts so that's the only reference in size I can go by so maybe hot topic and Spencers gifts runs big but I feel like it's this set that runs a bit small rather than 2 stores and 3 different brands of tapers and plugs that run big. So just use your brain don't force plugs that won't go in with ease into your lobes and buy a set of 00g tapers or what ever size you are planning to stop at and use those before trying to get those awesome new plugs you just bought into your ears.. take it from me infections suck bad! I just went through it and it was an awful couple of weeks on and off antibiotics and back and forth to the drs. So smart and happy stretching folks! Below is a photo of the 00g from this set and a 00g taper I bought at hot topic (morbid metals brand)

product_title: KONOV Polished Stainless Steel Band Biker Men's Signet Ring,
review_body:
Get the ring to your actual ring size. Don't listen to anyone who says otherwise. They don't know what their ring sizes are. I took a keyring and used it to size my fingers, most of them fit easily, some had a squeeze. I measured, went to a legitimate chart, and ordered. The rings fit (four of them, all different, not even same brand). I will say this, don't order up. If you measure a 12 or think the size chart listed for the rings is a bit to the far end, get the smaller size. I have muscular and squat fingers, they fit fine for me at the larger end, especially when flexed.

I got a 12 in this ring even though it is below the expected size of the fingers I intend to wear it on. It fits them fine. Use an altered rule, round down unless you meet the requirement for the next size up or expect to flex that finger a lot.

If you just want a plain old shiny chunk on your fingers, you got it right here. The bottom of the ring is about half as wide as the top, so expect a good amount of wear time before you go through this unit.

product_title: MAZU Zircon Ring AA+ Quality Top125 Color Rose Gold
review_headline: Picture is slightly different than product but still high quality.
review_body:
I really loved the design of this ring. Only the actual product is slightly different than the picture. The petals of the ring are flatter and much more pointed down than the picture. I expected the color to be like black hills gold, however, it is more like brass. For this, I was about to give it 3 stars. However, the ring is really nice in quality. The base is brass, which leads to the brass looking color. I have warn the ring for the day and it has been a very busy day. The ring has held up nicely. I have bought a wedding ring from eBay that was hundreds more that broke on day one doing the laundry. So, for that, I gave it 4 stars. Not to mention, the size is perfect for me and my daughter and I have had absolutely no allergy issues which says A LOT. I break out form many things that says they are allergy friendly but this ring has turned out to be great!!

****I bought this product at a discount for my honest review.*****

review_body: This is a really cute necklace, but it is surprisingly large. As a result, it isn't as classy as some of the other necklaces I have seen. I would give this to my 15 yr old niece, for instance, but not for me. The writing and Peace symbol isn't super delicate, so you can really read it clearly. It is definitely cute, but a little more juvenile than other necklaces. Definitely a great gift for a young adult who is into the Peace symbol, which seems to be everywhere again!

product_title: 1XS2DI32SS Earspiral tm Earrings Sterling Silver
review_headline: These ear spirals are delicate and pretty and I literally forget I'm wearing them
review_body: I got my first pair of Harry Mason earrings nearly 20 years ago!  These ear spirals are delicate and pretty and I literally forget I'm wearing them, they are so lightweight!  I have very small/narrow piercings and some earring wires are too big in diameter that I can't wear them or they are uncomfortable.  Never had a problem with any HM earrings - they slide right through.  These have become my everyday earrings - try them and they'll probably become yours, too.
